{"type":"message","id":"46f40028","parentId":"f6f631c1","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:44:15.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我来读取 `index.html` 中的 `toggleRegionMode` 函数和 `_finishRegion` 函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_21fc6a255ce64e3d9fe40b31","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":2853,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":47473,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783359846157,"responseId":"cht000def11@dx19f3887cbe22872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1c80ab2","parentId":"46f40028","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:44:15.715Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_21fc6a255ce64e3d9fe40b31","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\r\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setFocusMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _getOverlayPos(e) {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var rect = overlay.getBoundingClientRect();\r\n        return { x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        \r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n        \r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n        \r\n        // v8.41: 搜索启动时启用停止按钮\r\n        var stopBtnId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btnWbLocalStop' : 'btnFocusLocalStop';\r\n        var stopBtn = document.getElementById(stopBtnId);\r\n        if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = false; stopBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n\n[128 more lines in file. Use offset=2953 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783359855715}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf5a14f2","parentId":"c1c80ab2","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:44:20.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_439f18ef42a248268cde4865","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":2953,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":48659,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48706,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783359855717,"responseId":"cht000d0814@dx19f3887e73929bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"01a618cc","parentId":"bf5a14f2","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:44:20.669Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_439f18ef42a248268cde4865","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '开始, ' + ev.crop, 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'wb') {\r\n                                    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain\r\n                                        + ' → R=' + ev.r_avg + ' G=' + ev.g_avg + ' B=' + ev.b_avg\r\n                                        + ' (Δ=' + ev.delta + ')', 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast\r\n                                        + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                        // 刷新主控台白平衡滑动条\r\n                                        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed) { wbRed.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    } else {\r\n                                        var rollMsg = ev.rollback_steps ? ' (回滚' + ev.rollback_steps + '步)' : '';\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                    }\r\n                                    // v8.41: 搜索完成后恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'cleanup') {\r\n                                    operationLog('清理完成', 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '失败: ' + ev.message, 'error');\r\n                                    showToast('error', label + '失败');\r\n                                    // v8.41: 搜索失败后恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'interrupt') {\r\n                                    // v8.41: 用户停止\r\n                                    operationLog(label + ': ' + ev.message, 'warning');\r\n                                    showToast('warning', label + '已停止');\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        var wbRed2 = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue2 = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal2 = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal2 = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed2) { wbRed2.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal2) wbRedVal2.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue2) { wbBlue2.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal2) wbBlueVal2.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    }\r\n                                    // 恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                }\r\n                            } catch(e) { /* 跳过损坏的 JSON */ }\r\n                        }\r\n                        return pump();\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n                return pump();\r\n            })\r\n            .catch(function(e) {\r\n                operationLog(label + '异常: ' + e.message, 'error');\r\n                showToast('error', '异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                // v8.41: 恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n            });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _resetRegionUI() {\r\n        _regionMode = null;\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (overlay) overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (box) box.style.display = 'none';\r\n\n[48 more lines in file. Use offset=3033 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783359860669}}
{"type":"message","id":"44be8a56","parentId":"01a618cc","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:46:04.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据我读取的代码和console.html中的按钮定义，我现在可以精简回答这3个问题：\n\n1. **主控台总共有多少个入口，框选对焦启动的时候，指向多少个脚本？**\n   - **硬按钮入口（手动模式）**：\n     - console.html 第304-305行：`ptzFocus('far')` 和 `ptzFocus('near')` 按钮 → 调用 `apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/manual-move', {...})`\n   - **框选入口（局部模式）**：\n     - console.html 第311行：`toggleRegionMode('focus')` 按钮 → 触发 `_finishRegion()` → POST `/api/v1/vision/focus-search`\n   - **脚本文档**：\n     - `get_exposure_time(client)` → 读取Shutter + minShutterLevelLimit + maxShutterLevelLimit → 计算慢快门倍率\n     - `calc_stable_delay(client)` → `exposure_time * 2 + 0.5s`\n   - **best3 逻辑**（autofocus.py 的 ContrastAF）**：\n     - `_best3_value` 在精调阶段更新：`if contrast > self._best3_value: self._best3_value = contrast`\n       - 发生位置：`_step_approach()` 第165行，每次采样后都检查\n     - 返回值：`DONE` 阶段时，通过 `cmd.get(\"best3\", cmd[\"contrast\"])` 返回给 FocusSearcher\n\n我已确认所有流程和脚本调用细节，可以精简回答。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"根据代码分析，给出精简报告：\n\n## 📋 主控台对焦入口总览\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 老板您好！                          │\n│ 主控台有2个对焦入口                  │\n│ 1. 硬按钮（手动）→1个API调用          │\n│ 2. 框选（局部）→executeScheduledSearch │\n│ → POST /api/v1/vision/focus-search │\n│                                     │\n│ 2. 现在计算best是什么流程？           │\n│ best1在粗调阶段持续更新              │\n│ best3精调阶段持续更新（每次采样）     │\n│                                     │\n│ 3. 计算延迟的方式？                  │\n│ 延迟 = 实际曝光时间 × 2 + 0.5s       │\n│ ✓ 涉及慢快门计算（慢快门开启时）      │\n│ ✓ 使用get_exposure_time计算曝光时间  │\n│                                     │\n│ 请指示！                            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n**问题1：主控台对焦入口 = 2个**\n- 硬按钮入口（手动模式）：`console.html:304-305` → `ptzFocus('far'|'near')` → 1个API (`/focus/manual-move`)\n- 框选入口（局部模式）：`console.html:311` → `toggleRegionMode('focus')` → 2个脚本（`ContrastAF` + `FocusSearcher`）\n\n**问题2：best计算时机**\n- `best1` **粗调阶段持续更新**（`autofocus.py:99-103`，每当 `contrast > _best1_value`）\n- `best3` **精调阶段持续更新**（`autofocus.py:165-166`，每次采样后都检查 `contrast > _best3_value`）\n- `best3` **最终返回**在 `DONE` 阶段（`autofocus.py:116-117`）\n\n**问题3：画面计算延迟（✓涉及慢快门）**\n- `calc_stable_delay(client)` = `get_exposure_time(client) * 2 + 0.5s`\n- `get_exposure_time(client)` 读取 `ShutterLevel`，**如果慢快门开启** → 读取 `minShutterLevelLimit` / `maxShutterLevelLimit` → 计算倍率 → **实际曝光时间 = base × (max_time / base_time)**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":50340,"output":922,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783359860670,"responseId":"cht000dfa55@dx19f38881ac82872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7609923d","parentId":"44be8a56","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:51:08.245Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47603\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 01:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n延迟 = 实际曝光时间 × 2 + 0.5s\n这是延迟0.5s截图+计算，还是立刻截图+延迟0.5s+计算？\n慢快门的计算逻辑是怎么样的？从哪里读取慢快门数据，给我范例"}],"timestamp":1783360268238}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3d4adb5","parentId":"7609923d","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:51:59.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know:\n1. Is the delay \"screenshot after 0.5s\" or \"immediate screenshot + delay 0.5s + calculate\"?\n2. How does the slow shutter calculation work? Where does it read slow shutter data from? Give an example.\n\nLet me re-read the relevant code in autofocus.py and region_base.py to answer precisely.\n\nFrom autofocus.py `run()`:\n```python\n# 移动\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._move_focus, cmd[\"action\"], cmd[\"duration\"])\nawait asyncio.sleep(cmd[\"duration\"])\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\ndelay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\nawait asyncio.sleep(delay)  # 等待稳定\n# 重新截图\nbgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n```\n\nSo the sequence is:\n1. Move focus\n2. Sleep for cmd[\"duration\"] (0.2s coarse or 0.05s fine)\n3. Stop focus\n4. Calculate delay = calc_stable_delay(client) \n5. Sleep for delay (等待稳定)\n6. Capture screenshot\n\nSo it's: move → wait duration → stop → wait delay → screenshot → calculate contrast\n\nThe delay is \"wait for stable\" AFTER stop and BEFORE screenshot.\n\nFrom region_base.py:\n```python\ndef get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    # GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter\n    # Read ShutterLevel, minShutterLevelLimit, maxShutterLevelLimit\n    # base_exposure = parse(ShutterLevel)\n    # If min_limit != max_limit → slow shutter is on\n    #   slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure\n    #   return base_exposure * slow_ratio\n    # return base_exposure\n\ndef calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    exposure = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return exposure * 2 + 0.5  # BASE_STABLE_DELAY = 0.5\n```\n\nLet me give a concrete example:\n- ShutterLevel = \"1/25\" → base_exposure = 0.04s\n- minShutterLevelLimit = \"1/25\", maxShutterLevelLimit = \"1/1\" → slow shutter on\n- min_time = 1/25 = 0.04s, max_time = 1/1 = 1.0s\n- slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure = 1.0 / 0.04 = 25\n- actual exposure = 0.04 * 25 = 1.0s\n- delay = 1.0 * 2 + 0.5 = 2.5s\n\nWait, that doesn't seem right. Let me re-read the code more carefully.\n\n```python\nif min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n    min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n    max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n    if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n        slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure if base_exposure > 0 else 1.0\n        return base_exposure * slow_ratio\n```\n\nSo:\n- base_exposure = _parse_shutter_level(shutter_level)  # e.g. 1/25 = 0.04\n- If min_limit != max_limit:\n  - min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n  - max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n  - slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure\n  - return base_exposure * slow_ratio\n\nWait, this is `base_exposure * (max_time / base_exposure)` = `max_time`. So the actual exposure time returned is just `max_time`?\n\nThat seems like a bug or redundant calculation. `base_exposure * (max_time / base_exposure)` simplifies to `max_time`.\n\nActually wait, let me think about this more carefully. The ShutterLevel is the current shutter speed. The min/max limits define the range. If slow shutter is on, the actual exposure could be anywhere from min to max. But the code uses `max_time` as the actual exposure, which is the worst case (longest exposure). This is used for calculating the stable delay, so using the max is conservative.\n\nBut the formula `base_exposure * slow_ratio` where `slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure` simplifies to `max_time`. So it's just returning `max_time`.\n\nLet me provide a concrete example for the user.\n\nExample 1: No slow shutter\n- ShutterLevel = \"1/60\" → base = 1/60 ≈ 0.01667s\n- minShutterLevelLimit = \"1/60\", maxShutterLevelLimit = \"1/60\" (same → no slow shutter)\n- Return: 0.01667s\n- Delay = 0.01667 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.5333s\n\nExample 2: With slow shutter (DSS)\n- ShutterLevel = \"1/25\" → base = 0.04s\n- minShutterLevelLimit = \"1/25\", maxShutterLevelLimit = \"1/1\"\n- min_time = 0.04, max_time = 1.0\n- slow_ratio = 1.0 / 0.04 = 25\n- return 0.04 * 25 = 1.0s\n- Delay = 1.0 * 2 + 0.5 = 2.5s\n\nActually, I need to be more careful. The ShutterLevel might not equal min_limit. Let me think about what these values actually mean.\n\nIn Hikvision ISAPI:\n- ShutterLevel = current shutter speed\n- minShutterLevelLimit = the fastest shutter speed allowed\n- maxShutterLevelLimit = the slowest shutter speed allowed\n\nWhen slow shutter (DSS) is enabled, the maxShutterLevelLimit extends to slower speeds. So the actual exposure could be up to maxShutterLevelLimit.\n\nThe code reads ShutterLevel (current) and checks if min != max. If they differ, it calculates:\n- slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure\n- actual = base * slow_ratio = max_time\n\nSo it's returning max_time, which is the maximum possible exposure time. This makes sense for delay calculation - use worst case.\n\nLet me present this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"从代码中提取精确流程：\n\n## 1. 延迟时序\n\n```\n移动对焦 → sleep(duration) → 停止对焦 → calc_stable_delay → sleep(delay) → 截图 → 计算反差\n```\n\n**不是立刻截图**。完整时序（`autofocus.py:218-225`）：\n\n```python\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._move_focus, cmd[\"action\"], cmd[\"duration\"])  # ① 发送移动指令\nawait asyncio.sleep(cmd[\"duration\"])      # ② 等待移动完成 (0.2s粗调 / 0.05s精调)\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus) # ③ 停止对焦\ndelay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)  # ④ 计算延迟\nawait asyncio.sleep(delay)                # ⑤ 等待画面稳定\nbgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)  # ⑥ 截图\n# 然后下一轮 step() 计算 contrast\n```\n\n所以是：**停止 → 等 delay 秒 → 截图 → 计算**\n\n---\n\n## 2. 慢快门计算逻辑\n\n**数据来源**：`GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter`（`region_base.py:68-103`）\n\n设备返回的 XML 结构（范例）：\n\n```xml\n<!-- 情况A：慢快门关闭 -->\n<Shutter>\n  <ShutterLevel>1/60</ShutterLevel>\n  <minShutterLevelLimit>1/60</minShutterLevelLimit>\n  <maxShutterLevelLimit>1/60</maxShutterLevelLimit>\n</Shutter>\n\n<!-- 情况B：慢快门开启（DSS倍率=25） -->\n<Shutter>\n  <ShutterLevel>1/25</ShutterLevel>\n  <minShutterLevelLimit>1/25</minShutterLevelLimit>\n  <maxShutterLevelLimit>1/1</maxShutterLevelLimit>   ← 不同！\n</Shutter>\n```\n\n**计算逻辑**：\n\n```\nbase_exposure = parse(ShutterLevel)          # 当前快门值\n\nif minLimit != maxLimit:                     # 慢快门开启\n    min_time = parse(minShutterLevelLimit)\n    max_time = parse(maxShutterLevelLimit)\n    slow_ratio = max_time / base_exposure\n    实际曝光 = base_exposure × slow_ratio    # 实际 = max_time\nelse:\n    实际曝光 = base_exposure\n\n延迟 = 实际曝光 × 2 + 0.5s\n```\n\n**范例计算**：\n\n| 场景 | ShutterLevel | minLimit | maxLimit | 实际曝光 | 延迟 |\n|------|-------------|----------|----------|---------|------|\n| 无慢快门 | 1/60 | 1/60 | 1/60 | 0.0167s | 0.53s |\n| 无慢快门 | 1/25 | 1/25 | 1/25 | 0.04s | 0.58s |\n| 慢快门×4 | 1/25 | 1/25 | 1/6 | 0.167s | 0.83s |\n| 慢快门×25 | 1/25 | 1/25 | 1/1 | 1.0s | 2.5s |\n| 慢快门×50 | 1/50 | 1/50 | 1/1 | 1.0s | 2.5s |\n\n⚠️ **注意**：`base_exposure × (max_time / base_exposure)` 数学上等于 `max_time`。代码写法冗余，实际返回的就是 `maxShutterLevelLimit` 对应的曝光时间。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":41603,"output":2223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43826,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783360268246,"responseId":"cht000d6eb9@dx19f388e308c2871503"}}
