{"type":"message","id":"130aa9d3","parentId":"57ca2a5c","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:57:09.894Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d50ead021cc546e4ae35a590","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: scrapling\r\ndescription: \"Adaptive web scraping framework with anti-bot bypass and spider crawling.\"\r\nversion: \"1.0.8\"\r\nmetadata:\r\n  {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"???\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"python3\"]}, \"tags\":[\"web-scraping\", \"crawling\", \"research\", \"automation\"]}}\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Scrapling - Adaptive Web Scraping\r\n\r\n> \"Effortless web scraping for the modern web.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Credits\r\n\r\n### Core Library\r\n- **Repository:** https://github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapling\r\n- **Author:** D4Vinci (Karim Shoair)\r\n- **License:** BSD-3-Clause\r\n- **Documentation:** https://scrapling.readthedocs.io\r\n\r\n### API Reverse Engineering Methodology\r\n- **GitHub:** https://github.com/paoloanzn/free-solscan-api\r\n- **X Post:** https://x.com/paoloanzn/status/2026361234032046319\r\n- **Author:** @paoloanzn\r\n- **Insight:** \"Web scraping is 80% reverse engineering\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# Core library (parser only)\r\npip install scrapling\r\n\r\n# With fetchers (HTTP + browser automation) - RECOMMENDED\r\npip install \"scrapling[fetchers]\"\r\nscrapling install\r\n\r\n# With shell (CLI tools) - RECOMMENDED\r\npip install \"scrapling[shell]\"\r\n\r\n# With AI (MCP server) - OPTIONAL\r\npip install \"scrapling[ai]\"\r\n\r\n# Everything\r\npip install \"scrapling[all]\"\r\n\r\n# Browser for stealth/dynamic mode\r\nplaywright install chromium\r\n\r\n# For Cloudflare bypass (advanced)\r\npip install cloudscraper\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Agent Instructions\r\n\r\n### When to Use Scrapling\r\n\r\n**Use Scrapling when:**\r\n- Research topics from websites\r\n- Extract data from blogs, news sites, docs\r\n- Crawl multiple pages with Spider\r\n- Gather content for summaries\r\n- Extract brand data from any website\r\n- Reverse engineer APIs from websites\r\n\r\n**Do NOT use for:**\r\n- X/Twitter (use x-tweet-fetcher skill)\r\n- Login-protected sites (unless credentials provided)\r\n- Paywalled content (respect robots.txt)\r\n- Sites that prohibit scraping in their TOS\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Quick Commands"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":379,"aggregated":"---\r\nname: scrapling\r\ndescription: \"Adaptive web scraping framework with anti-bot bypass and spider crawling.\"\r\nversion: \"1.0.8\"\r\nmetadata:\r\n  {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"???\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"python3\"]}, \"tags\":[\"web-scraping\", \"crawling\", \"research\", \"automation\"]}}\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Scrapling - Adaptive Web Scraping\r\n\r\n> \"Effortless web scraping for the modern web.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Credits\r\n\r\n### Core Library\r\n- **Repository:** https://github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapling\r\n- **Author:** D4Vinci (Karim Shoair)\r\n- **License:** BSD-3-Clause\r\n- **Documentation:** https://scrapling.readthedocs.io\r\n\r\n### API Reverse Engineering Methodology\r\n- **GitHub:** https://github.com/paoloanzn/free-solscan-api\r\n- **X Post:** https://x.com/paoloanzn/status/2026361234032046319\r\n- **Author:** @paoloanzn\r\n- **Insight:** \"Web scraping is 80% reverse engineering\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# Core library (parser only)\r\npip install scrapling\r\n\r\n# With fetchers (HTTP + browser automation) - RECOMMENDED\r\npip install \"scrapling[fetchers]\"\r\nscrapling install\r\n\r\n# With shell (CLI tools) - RECOMMENDED\r\npip install \"scrapling[shell]\"\r\n\r\n# With AI (MCP server) - OPTIONAL\r\npip install \"scrapling[ai]\"\r\n\r\n# Everything\r\npip install \"scrapling[all]\"\r\n\r\n# Browser for stealth/dynamic mode\r\nplaywright install chromium\r\n\r\n# For Cloudflare bypass (advanced)\r\npip install cloudscraper\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Agent Instructions\r\n\r\n### When to Use Scrapling\r\n\r\n**Use Scrapling when:**\r\n- Research topics from websites\r\n- Extract data from blogs, news sites, docs\r\n- Crawl multiple pages with Spider\r\n- Gather content for summaries\r\n- Extract brand data from any website\r\n- Reverse engineer APIs from websites\r\n\r\n**Do NOT use for:**\r\n- X/Twitter (use x-tweet-fetcher skill)\r\n- Login-protected sites (unless credentials provided)\r\n- Paywalled content (respect robots.txt)\r\n- Sites that prohibit scraping in their TOS\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Quick Commands","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783360629894}}
{"type":"message","id":"649e6bfc","parentId":"130aa9d3","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:57:19.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我将使用多个搜索引擎来查找关于对比度检测自动对焦算法的最佳实践。我将并行地在多个引擎上进行搜索。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e60fda57e2ef4f46bf6257f6","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":15000,"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=contrast+detection+autofocus+algorithm+best+practice+implementation"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_148ad884b90b425e92a85f4a","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":15000,"url":"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=contrast+detection+autofocus+algorithm+peak+detection+climb+search"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_606cb6e614f04dde8d79b758","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":15000,"url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=contrast+detection+autofocus+algorithm+implementation&ensearch=1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":46790,"output":155,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783360629895,"responseId":"cht000dce4b@dx19f3893c0232872503"}}
