ease this upcoming season by jena or jonesville does anyone know of one i can get into or have some land i can...\\n- ## [Clear lake - Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=be661a018ab5996546aff286faf6988cc25770d435a962be660426ddd26f6185JmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL2NsZWFyLWxha2UuMTAzODA2Lw&ntb=1)\\nSep 28, 2009 · I aint had a chance to do any scouting this year. Anyone been out to Clear lake WMA I just need to know if there is any water or ducks out there. Any info would help thanks.\\n- ## [sculling | Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=29da86394ab2fc26d73fb510791303c4c7f184dd33d4903a2cc2465c01377b0aJmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL3NjdWxsaW5nLjcyOTM3Lw&ntb=1)\\nOct 2, 2008 · Is sculling a legal method of hunting in North Carolina? Last year my son and I hunted the Pamlico Sound and we saw hundreds of Brant all rafted up on the reef. They would stay well out of …\\n- ## [Opener - Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=b7af12b3297476c241755f16544cffc23d273620e33ab2ec022a11cf27ecdcf3JmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL29wZW5lci4xMDY0OTYv&ntb=1)\\nOct 25, 2009 · Went to little dry creek for the opener, got a blind and we couldn't get the mallards to work. They were there, landing in the end of the pond but wouldn't fly over the blind. We were also to …\\n- ## [gps - Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=5f4423e4aa7deaec2ede2a7db5b22ae92a16018671e082b1f8e95fd0d428e13eJmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL2dwcy4xMDUwOTMv&ntb=1)\\nOct 11, 2009 · hey I need to buy a new gps the last one i had i bought in 1998(outdated).I hunt in the everglades so im looking for a unit that will record me exact track so i can get back in there in the …\\n- ## [Mille Lacs - Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=f1e5a789f543dd74eecef8646061e3b7fff77ef365527cd81e38a329ec919683JmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL21pbGxlLWxhY3MuMTA2NjQ1Lw&ntb=1)\\nOct 26, 2009 · I've heard that late season, Mille Lacs can be a really good lake for divers (especially golden eye). If anyone knows about hunting the lake, please PM me or write back here. Thanks\\n- ## [thinking about getting a boat for the Delta | Duck Hunting Forum](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=93cbae6c7bf91398f3dc1fd693753b2fb7a6d6b4277c62902aea28dd6d4fe5afJmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZHVja2h1bnRpbmdjaGF0LmNvbS90aHJlYWRzL3RoaW5raW5nLWFib3V0LWdldHRpbmctYS1ib2F0LWZvci10aGUtZGVsdGEuMTU5MDE3Lw&ntb=1)\\nAug 24, 2011 · Hunting the delta in the winter and inclimate weather in a 12 foot boat with 2 men, a dog and equipment is a good way to die. That would be a totally overloaded boat, a dangerous situation.\\n- Some results are removed in response to a notice of local law requirement. For more information, please see [here](https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=05cf7a79eb1a55d7d2c6450d5748a1f787d52cceb89f5bd782fe3ad7a506ad81JmltdHM9MTc4MzI5NjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0de2b9ba-4ffb-694a-2488-ae344eb86896&u=a1aHR0cDovL2dvLm1pY3Jvc29mdC5jb20vZndsaW5rLz9MaW5rSUQ9NjE3MzUw&ntb=1).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0491ec26abcbc181\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=autofocus+contrast+detection+hill+climbing+algorithm+focus+measure+Laplacian+variance&ensearch=1","finalUrl":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=autofocus+contrast+detection+hill+climbing+algorithm+focus+measure+Laplacian+variance&ensearch=1","status":200,"contentType":"