{"type":"message","id":"920cb53b","parentId":"8f3affc8","timestamp":"2026-07-06T19:06:03.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"功能，删除工作已完成。现在翻译成中文精简报告：\n- 显示关键步骤\n- 说明“验证失败”原因（110.5/138.4 不达标）\n- 附截图路径\n- 不多废话\n\n匹配用户要求的精简风格：\n- 中文\n- 逻辑图或要点\n- 不扩展展示细节\n- 直到最后给截图路径反馈","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 自动对焦执行完成（v8.59, 画面中间30%）\n\n```\n设备: 192.168.5.72 (4k 32X DC)\n区域: 画面中间30% (crop X=1344~2495, Y=756~1403, 744k 像素)\n\n步骤:\n  1. [scan] 近→近→近 (反差上升: 138 → 138 = best)\n  2. [scan] 近 (下降: 138 → 108)\n  3. [approach] 远退3.09步 → 峰值处\n  4. [done] 验证\n```\n\n结果：\n- 峰值 (best_contrast): 138.44\n- 对焦后 (final_contrast): 115.17\n- 验证: **FAIL** (115.17 < 138.44 × 0.95)\n\n说明：验证失败。脚距移动后反差未恢复到≥131.5（峰值×0.95）\n\n截图已保存：tmp_af_screenshot.png"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":118223,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118543,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783364718146,"responseId":"cht000d75bf@dx19f38d216322871503"}}
