{"type":"message","id":"b29119df","parentId":"48f2224b","timestamp":"2026-07-06T19:43:57.751Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"修改完成了么？\"。我之前的回复只是分析了bug和给出了修复方案，但并没有实际执行修改。我需要立即执行修改。\n\n根据我的分析，核心bug有3个：\n1. **样条振荡**：Test2数据（5点，反差波动小）导致三次样条产生3个局部极值，黄金分割搜索找到的是虚假峰值\n2. **步长线性假设错误**：`move_duration = abs(delta) * 0.2` 假设电机移动距离与时间成正比，但电机的加速/减速阶段使得短脉冲（0.2s）和长脉冲（0.6s）的移动距离不成比例\n3. **缺少R²质量检验**：拟合前未检查数据质量\n\n修复方案（最小修改）：\n1. 在 `_fit_and_search` 中添加 R² 检验，不达标则回退到 simple best\n2. 回退时用多步 0.2s 离散移动代替一次性长移动（解决步长线性问题）\n3. 缩小黄金分割搜索区间到峰值附近\n\n让我现在执行修改。我需要仔细修改 autofocus.py 中的 `_fit_and_search` 方法和 `APPROACH` 状态处理。\n\n具体修改：\n1. `_fit_and_search` 中：\n   - 添加 R² 检验\n   - 缩小搜索区间\n   - 返回回退步数（整数），而不是浮点数\n\n2. `APPROACH` 状态：\n   - 改为多步回退（每步0.2s），而不是一次性回退\n   - 需要 tracking 剩余步数\n\n让我重新设计 `_fit_and_search` 和 `_step_approach`：\n\n```python\ndef _fit_and_search(self):\n    \"\"\"三次样条拟合 + 黄金分割搜索。\"\"\"\n    x_vals = [p[0] for p in self._points]\n    y_vals = [p[1] for p in self._points]\n\n    # 数据点不足 → 回退\n    if len(x_vals) < 4:\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    # R²质量检验 → 低质量回退\n    r2 = self._calc_r2()\n    if r2 is not None and r2 < 0.6:\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    # 拟合样条\n    spline = CubicSpline(x_vals, y_vals)\n    if spline._coeffs is None:\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    # 黄金分割搜索（缩小到峰值附近±2步）\n    best_idx = self._best_pos\n    x_low = max(x_vals[0], best_idx - 2)\n    x_up = min(x_vals[-1], best_idx + 2)\n    \n    candidates = []\n    for (lo, hi) in [(x_low, x_up)]:\n        try:\n            opt = golden_section_search(spline, lo, hi)\n            candidates.append(opt)\n        except:\n            pass\n\n    if not candidates:\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n    self._best_value = opt_y\n    self._optimal_pos = opt_x\n\n    # 计算回退步数（整数，每步0.2s）\n    current_pos = x_vals[-1]\n    delta = current_pos - opt_x  # 需要回退的步数\n\n    if abs(delta) < 0.5:\n        # 已在峰值附近\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    # 离散回退：每步0.2s\n    self._approach_remaining = int(round(abs(delta)))\n    self._approach_dir = -self._direction  # 回退方向\n    \n    if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {...}\n\n    action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n    self._state = self.APPROACH\n    \n    return {\n        \"action\": action,\n        \"duration\": 0.2,\n        \"stage\": \"approach\",\n        \"contrast\": round(self._points[-1][1], 2),\n        \"message\": f\"样条峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},回退{self._approach_remaining}步\"\n    }\n\ndef _step_approach(self, contrast):\n    \"\"\"逐步回退到峰值位置。\"\"\"\n    self._approach_remaining -= 1\n    \n    if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n        # 回退完成\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n            \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n            \"best\": self._best_value\n        }\n    \n    # 继续回退\n    action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n    return {\n        \"action\": action,\n        \"duration\": 0.2,\n        \"stage\": \"approach\",\n        \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n        \"message\": f\"逼近(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步,峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\"\n    }\n```\n\n这样修改：\n1. 添加 R² 检验（<0.6 回退到 simple best）\n2. 缩小黄金分割搜索区间到峰值附近±2步\n3. 回退改为多步0.2s离散移动（与扫描步长一致，消除电机非线性）\n4. 验证容差保持0.95（因为现在是离散回退，应该更精确）\n\n让我在 `__init__` 中也要添加 `_approach_remaining` 和 `_approach_dir` 的初始化。\n\n现在让我执行修改。我需要：\n1. 修改 `__init__` 方法（添加新字段）\n2. 修改 `_fit_and_search` 方法\n3. 修改 `_step_approach` 方法\n\n让我用 edit 工具精确修改。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"还没改，现在立即执行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_35f3c1013862405cb8e50fcd","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"oldText":"        # 平坦区域\n        self._flat_reversed = False\n\n        # 结果\n        self._optimal_pos = None","newText":"        # 平坦区域\n        self._flat_reversed = False\n\n        # 结果\n        self._optimal_pos = None\n        self._approach_remaining = 0\n        self._approach_dir = 1"},{"oldText":"    def _fit_and_search(self):\n        \"\"\"三次样条拟合 + 黄金分割搜索。\"\"\"\n        x_vals = [p[0] for p in self._points]\n        y_vals = [p[1] for p in self._points]\n\n        # 数据点不足 → 回退到简单 best\n        if len(x_vals) < 4:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(数据不足,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 拟合样条\n        spline = CubicSpline(x_vals, y_vals)\n        if spline._coeffs is None:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(样条拟合失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 黄金分割搜索（3个区间取最优）\n        x_low = x_vals[0]\n        x_up = x_vals[-1]\n        x_mid = (x_low + x_up) / 2\n\n        candidates = []\n        for (lo, hi) in [(x_low, x_mid), (x_mid, x_up), (x_low, x_up)]:\n            try:\n                opt = golden_section_search(spline, lo, hi)\n                candidates.append(opt)\n            except Exception:\n                pass\n\n        if not candidates:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(搜索失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n        self._best_value = opt_y\n        self._optimal_pos = opt_x\n\n        # 计算移动到峰值位置的参数\n        current_pos = x_vals[-1]\n        delta = current_pos - opt_x  # 需要回退的步数\n\n        if abs(delta) < 0.1:\n            # 已在峰值附近\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(opt_y, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},已在峰值)\",\n                \"best\": opt_y\n            }\n\n        # 计算移动参数：回退 delta 步，每步 0.2s\n        move_dir = -self._direction  # 回退方向\n        move_duration = abs(delta) * 0.2\n        action = \"focus_near\" if move_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n\n        self._state = self.APPROACH\n\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"duration\": round(move_duration, 3),\n            \"stage\": \"approach\",\n            \"contrast\": round(self._points[-1][1], 2),\n            \"message\": f\"样条峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},移动{abs(delta):.2f}步\"\n        }","newText":"    def _fit_and_search(self):\n        \"\"\"三次样条拟合 + 黄金分割搜索。\"\"\"\n        x_vals = [p[0] for p in self._points]\n        y_vals = [p[1] for p in self._points]\n\n        # 数据点不足 → 回退到简单 best\n        if len(x_vals) < 4:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(数据不足,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # R²质量检验 → 低质量回退到 simple best\n        r2 = self._calc_r2()\n        if r2 is not None and r2 < 0.6:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(R²={r2:.2f}<0.6,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 拟合样条\n        spline = CubicSpline(x_vals, y_vals)\n        if spline._coeffs is None:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(样条拟合失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 黄金分割搜索（缩小到峰值附近±2步，避免样条振荡区）\n        best_idx = self._best_pos\n        x_low = max(x_vals[0], best_idx - 2)\n        x_up = min(x_vals[-1], best_idx + 2)\n\n        candidates = []\n        try:\n            opt = golden_section_search(spline, x_low, x_up)\n            candidates.append(opt)\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n        if not candidates:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(搜索失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n        self._best_value = opt_y\n        self._optimal_pos = opt_x\n\n        # 计算回退步数（整数，每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）\n        current_pos = x_vals[-1]\n        delta = current_pos - opt_x  # 需要回退的步数\n\n        if abs(delta) < 0.5:\n            # 已在峰值附近\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(opt_y, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},已在峰值)\",\n                \"best\": opt_y\n            }\n\n        # 离散回退：每步0.2s（与扫描步长一致，消除电机非线性）\n        self._approach_remaining = int(round(abs(delta)))\n        self._approach_dir = -self._direction  # 回退方向\n\n        if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(opt_y, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f})\",\n                \"best\": opt_y\n            }\n\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        self._state = self.APPROACH\n\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"duration\": 0.2,\n            \"stage\": \"approach\",\n            \"contrast\": round(self._points[-1][1], 2),\n            \"message\": f\"样条峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},回退{self._approach_remaining}步\"\n        }"},{"oldText":"    def _step_approach(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"移动到峰值后验证。\"\"\"\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n            \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n            \"best\": self._best_value\n        }","newText":"    def _step_approach(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"逐步回退到峰值位置（每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）。\"\"\"\n        self._approach_remaining -= 1\n\n        if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n            # 回退完成\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 继续回退\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"duration\": 0.2,\n            \"stage\": \"approach\",\n            \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"逼近(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步,峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\"\n        }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":127570,"output":3864,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783366968300,"responseId":"cht000d87a4@dx19f38f4b3e529c2503"}}
