{"type":"message","id":"bdde5d9e","parentId":"2f928234","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:06:14.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right. Let me trace through this carefully:\n\nScan data (focus_near):\n```\npos 0: 79.97   (step 1)\npos 1: 87.71   (step 2) - rising\npos 2: 97.49   (step 3) - rising\npos 3: 160.00  (step 4) - rising\npos 4: 329.41  (step 5) - PEAK! best=329.4\npos 5: 120.70  (step 6) - declining (decline_after_best=1)\npos 6: 94.01   (step 7) - declining (decline_after_best=2)\n```\n\nAt step 7 (pos=6), decline_after_best=2, not yet 3. So the algorithm continues scanning.\n\nStep 8: FocusSearcher moves focus_near 0.2s, waits, stops, delays, captures → new contrast=329.41\n\nWait, step 8's contrast is 329.41, same as step 5! But the done message says R²=0.51<0.6.\n\nActually wait, let me re-read:\n```\n[03:59:05] ◇ 对焦 #8: done stop 反差=329.41 (0s) 对焦成功(R²=0.51<0.6,使用best=329.4)\n```\n\nSo step 8: contrast=329.41, and the algorithm triggers _fit_and_search because decline_after_best reaches 3.\n\nWait, but decline_after_best was 2 at step 7. At step 8, contrast=329.41 which is LESS than best (329.4)... actually 329.41 > 329.4? Let me check: the code stores _best_value as a float. At step 5, contrast=329.41, so _best_value=329.41 (stored as float). At step 8, contrast=329.41 again. Is 329.41 > 329.41? No, it's equal. So is_new_best=False, and decline_after_best becomes 3.\n\nSo at step 8 (pos=7): decline_after_best=3, best=329.41 > 100 → triggers _fit_and_search!\n\nIn _fit_and_search:\n- x_vals = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]\n- y_vals = [79.97, 87.71, 97.49, 160.00, 329.41, 120.70, 94.01, 329.41]\n\nWait, pos 7 has contrast=329.41? That's the same as pos 4. But the user said the motor kept going focus_near... so how did it get back to the same contrast?\n\nActually, I think I misread. Let me re-read the log:\n\n```\n[03:59:05] ◇ 对焦 #8: done stop 反差=329.41 (0s) 对焦成功(R²=0.51<0.6,使用best=329.4)\n```\n\nThe \"反差=329.41\" in step 8 is the contrast computed from the captured frame. But wait, this is the done step. Let me trace more carefully:\n\nAfter step 7 (pos=6, contrast=94.01):\n- decline_after_best = 2 (steps 6 and 7 declined)\n- Not yet 3 → continue scanning\n- Returns \"focus_near, 0.2s\"\n- FocusSearcher: move focus_near 0.2s → sleep 0.2s → stop → delay → capture → new bgr\n\nStep 8:\n- contrast = calc_contrast(bgr) → 329.41\n- af.step(329.41):\n  - pos = 7\n  - _points.append((7, 329.41))\n  - 329.41 > _best_value (329.41)? No (equal). is_new_best = False\n  - _decline_after_best = 3 (was 2, now 3)\n  - Check: decline_after_best >= 3 AND best > 100 → YES! → _fit_and_search()\n\nIn _fit_and_search:\n- x_vals = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]\n- y_vals = [79.97, 87.71, 97.49, 160.00, 329.41, 120.70, 94.01, 329.41]\n\nNow R² is calculated. The data has TWO peaks at pos=4 and pos=7, both 329.41. This is clearly not a simple unimodal function. R² = 0.51 < 0.6 → fallback!\n\nR² fallback returns:\n```python\nself._state = self.DONE\nreturn {\n    \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n    \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n    \"message\": f\"对焦成功(R²={r2:.2f}<0.6,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n    \"best\": self._best_value\n}\n```\n\nThis returns \"stop\" at the current position (pos=7, which is the second 329.41 reading). But the verification capture shows 98.34.\n\nSo the motor is at pos=7 (7 steps of focus_near from start), but the real peak was at pos=4 (4 steps). The motor overshot by 3 steps!\n\nThe R² fallback doesn't move back to the best position. It just stops.\n\n**THE CORE BUG IS CLEAR NOW:**\n\nWhen R² < 0.6, the algorithm returns \"stop\" without moving to the best position. The motor is at pos=7 (3 steps past the real peak at pos=4), and the verification capture shows 98.34 (far from the peak).\n\nThe user is absolutely right: \"已经找到了焦点，但是实际并没有移动到焦点\" - the algorithm found the peak at pos=4, but didn't move to it. It stopped at pos=7.\n\nAnd: \"根本没有逼近真实的best，而是随意停在了98.34这种不知道哪里来的位置\" - the motor stopped at a random position (pos=7) which has real contrast=98.34.\n\n**THE FIX:**\n\nR² fallback should NOT just stop. It should:\n1. Calculate how many steps to move back to best_pos\n2. Return a move command (like the normal _fit_and_search path)\n3. Use the APPROACH state to step back to best_pos\n\nEssentially, the R² fallback should behave the same as the normal path - move to best_pos - just without the spline/golden section search.\n\nLet me fix this now.\n\nThe fix is simple: in the R² fallback, instead of returning \"stop\", calculate the return to best_pos and return an approach command.\n\n```python\n# R²质量检验 → 低质量：回退到 best_pos（不拟合样条）\nr2 = self._calc_r2()\nif r2 is not None and r2 < 0.6:\n    # 不做样条拟合，直接回退到 best_pos\n    current_pos = len(self._points) - 1\n    delta = current_pos - self._best_pos  # 需要回退的步数\n    \n    if abs(delta) < 1:\n        # 已在 best 附近\n        self._state = self.DONE\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n            \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"对焦成功(R²={r2:.2f}<0.6,已在best)\",\n            \"best\": self._best_value\n        }\n    \n    self._approach_remaining = abs(delta)\n    self._approach_dir = -self._direction\n    action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n    self._state = self.APPROACH\n    return {\n        \"action\": action,\n        \"duration\": 0.2,\n        \"stage\": \"approach\",\n        \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n        \"message\": f\"R²={r2:.2f}<0.6,回退到best(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步)\"\n    }\n```\n\nThis way, even when R² is low, the algorithm still moves back to the best position.\n\nAlso, I should fix the other bugs:\n1. Flat detection threshold: 20 → 10\n2. Decline detection: add cumulative decline ratio\n\nLet me also check: should I also fix the \"连续5步下降\" to something more robust?\n\nFor the波动数据 in Phase 1 (steps 1-20), the data fluctuates 65-77, never triggering _decline_count >= 5 (consecutive declines). A better approach would be: if best hasn't improved in N steps, reverse. This is simpler and more robust than tracking consecutive declines.\n\nActually, the existing _decline_after_best already tracks this! It counts steps after the best that didn't improve. If _decline_after_best >= some threshold, we should reverse.\n\nBut _decline_after_best is only used for the peak confirmation (>= 3 and best > 100). It's not used for the \"reverse\" logic. The reverse logic uses _decline_count >= 5 (consecutive).\n\nFor the flat region case, _decline_after_best keeps growing (since best never improves), but it's only checked against >= 3 with best > 100. If best <= 100 (like in the 65-77 range), the peak confirmation doesn't trigger.\n\nAnd the flat check only happens at step >= 20.\n\nSo the fix should be: if _decline_after_best >= 10 (no improvement for 10 steps) AND best <= 100, reverse.\n\nOr simpler: lower the flat detection threshold from 20 to 10.\n\nLet me fix all 3 bugs now:\n1. R² fallback: move to best_pos instead of stopping\n2. Flat detection: 20 → 10\n3. (Optional) Add _decline_after_best >= 10 check for low-best cases\n\nActually, the user's immediate concern is bug #1 (R² fallback not moving to best). Let me fix that first, plus the flat detection threshold.\n\nLet me execute the fix now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对。我定位到了核心bug：\n\n```\nscan 数据 (focus_near):\n  pos 0: 79.97\n  pos 1: 87.71\n  pos 2: 97.49\n  pos 3: 160.00\n  pos 4: 329.41  ← 真实峰值 (best)\n  pos 5: 120.70  ← 下降1\n  pos 6: 94.01   ← 下降2\n  pos 7: 329.41  ← 步8读数（触发R²=0.51<0.6）\n\nR²<0.6 → 直接 stop，不回退到 best_pos\n当前电机在 pos 7（过冲3步）→ 验证 98.34 ≠ best 329.4\n```\n\n**根因**：R² fallback 返回 `\"action\": \"stop\"`，不移动到 best_pos。电机停在过冲位置。\n\n立即修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c8a231f6211f4220a0b737ce","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":300,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":143599,"output":2562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783368291825,"responseId":"cht000d58ce@dx19f39090a1b2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"745d8428","parentId":"bdde5d9e","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:06:14.399Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c8a231f6211f4220a0b737ce","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"stage\": \"scan\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"采样(best={self._best_value:.1f},方向={dir_name})\"\n        }\n\n    def _fit_and_search(self):\n        \"\"\"三次样条拟合 + 黄金分割搜索。\"\"\"\n        x_vals = [p[0] for p in self._points]\n        y_vals = [p[1] for p in self._points]\n\n        # 数据点不足 → 回退到简单 best\n        if len(x_vals) < 4:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(数据不足,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # R²质量检验 → 低质量回退到 simple best\n        r2 = self._calc_r2()\n        if r2 is not None and r2 < 0.6:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(R²={r2:.2f}<0.6,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 拟合样条\n        spline = CubicSpline(x_vals, y_vals)\n        if spline._coeffs is None:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(样条拟合失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        # 黄金分割搜索（缩小到峰值附近±2步，避免样条振荡区）\n        best_idx = self._best_pos\n        x_low = max(x_vals[0], best_idx - 2)\n        x_up = min(x_vals[-1], best_idx + 2)\n\n        candidates = []\n        try:\n            opt = golden_section_search(spline, x_low, x_up)\n            candidates.append(opt)\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n        if not candidates:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(self._best_value, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(搜索失败,使用best={self._best_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best_value\n            }\n\n        opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n        self._best_value = opt_y\n        self._optimal_pos = opt_x\n\n        # 计算回退步数（整数，每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）\n        current_pos = x_vals[-1]\n        delta = current_pos - opt_x  # 需要回退的步数\n\n        if abs(delta) < 0.5:\n            # 已在峰值附近\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(opt_y, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(峰值={opt_y:.1f}@pos={opt_x:.2f},已在峰值)\",\n                \"best\": opt_y\n            }\n\n\n[219 more lines in file. Use offset=380 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783368374399}}
