{"type":"message","id":"b8121f33","parentId":"9c8a7be1","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:10:07.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改完成。\n\n## 修复报告\n\n```\n文件: src/controlpanel/autofocus.py (3处修复)\n```\n\n### Bug 1（核心）：R² fallback 不回退到 best_pos\n\n```\n修复前: R²<0.6 → 直接 stop → 电机停在过冲位置 → 验证失败\n修复后: R²<0.6 → 进入 APPROACH → 逐步回退到 best_pos → 验证\n\n同样修复了\"样条拟合失败\"和\"搜索失败\"两个 fallback\n所有 fallback 路径都回退到 best_pos，不再随意 stop\n```\n\n### Bug 2：平坦检测延迟\n\n```\n修复前: _step_count >= 20 才检查平坦 → 浪费10步\n修复后: _step_count >= 10 即检查\n```\n\n### 回归测试（模拟老板数据）\n\n```\nscan: 79→87→97→160→329(峰值)→120→94→329(触发)\nR²=0.36<0.6 → 回退3步到 best_pos\napproach: 3步回退 → done\n```\n\n需要重启 AstroHub 后实测。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":151174,"output":256,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783368583775,"responseId":"cht000dbb0d@dx19f390d4da929c2503"}}
