{"type":"message","id":"a1994db7","parentId":"f17fd1a5","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:19:07.347Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_91da6a845764417495c9dc2e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\r\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setFocusMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\n[188 more lines in file. Use offset=2893 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783369147347}}
{"type":"message","id":"f128782e","parentId":"a1994db7","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:19:24.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我现在完全理解了。让我执行这 项修改：\n\n**任务1**: `onFocusModeChange('local')` 时 → `setFocusMode('area')` (而不是 'manual')，且 `toggleRegionMode('focus')` 不再切换模式（因为已经在局部模式了）。\n\n**任务2**: APPROACH 分两阶段：0.2s 步进（best2）→ 0.1s 步进（best3，必须 > best2）。\n\n**任务3**: 阈值 100 → 50。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_29a7a3db6b07436896284bdf","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    } else if (mode === 'local') {\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\n        // v8.60: 局部模式直接设置 area 模式\n        setFocusMode('area');\n    } else {","oldText":"    } else if (mode === 'local') {\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\n        // v8.39: 局部模式自动切换到手动模式\n        setFocusMode('manual');\n    } else {"},{"newText":"        // v8.60: 局部模式已在 onFocusModeChange 中设置 area，框选不再切换\n        // if (mode === 'focus') {\n        //     var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n        //     if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\n        //         setFocusMode('manual');\n        //     }\n        // }","oldText":"        if (mode === 'focus') {\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\n                setFocusMode('manual');\n            }\n        }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":161394,"output":470,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783369147351,"responseId":"cht000d0774@dx19f3915b55829bb503"}}
