{"type":"message","id":"e8dfd5bf","parentId":"8c988863","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:34:25.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改完成。\n\n## 修改报告 (v8.59 → v8.60)\n\n```\n备份: backup_20260707_0415/\n修改: 3个文件，7处精确修改\n```\n\n### 任务1：局部对焦模式 → area\n```\n文件: console.html (onFocusModeChange)\n  旧: mode==='local' → setFocusMode('manual')\n  新: mode==='local' → setFocusMode('area')\n\n文件: index.html (toggleRegionMode)\n  旧: 点击框选时自动 setFocusMode('manual')\n  新: 删除该切换（已在 onChange 中设置 area）\n```\n\n### 任务2：APPROACH 后增加 0.1s 精逼近\n```\n文件: autofocus.py\n  新增状态: FINE\n  新增字段: _best2_value, _best3_value, _fine_step, _fine_dir, _fine_max_steps\n  \n  流程变更:\n    旧: SCAN → APPROACH(0.2s) → DONE\n    新: SCAN → APPROACH(0.2s) → FINE(0.1s, 最多10步) → DONE\n  \n  FINE 逻辑:\n    - best3 > best2 → 成功\n    - 趋势下降 → 反向\n    - 最多10步\n```\n\n### 任务3：阈值 100 → 50\n```\n文件: autofocus.py (2处)\n  峰值确认: best > 100 → best > 50\n  R²失败: best <= 100 → best <= 50\n```\n\n### 版本号\n```\nconstants.py: v8.59 → v8.60\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":176219,"output":368,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783370016594,"responseId":"cht000d1f3e@dx19f3923848f2872503"}}
