{"type":"message","id":"5441c7b7","parentId":"e86be5b6","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:42:47.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me carefully analyze the user's feedback:\n\n1. **精调结果比粗调差**: \n   - 粗调 best = 84.9 (step 26: 样条峰值=84.9@pos=12.16)\n   - 精调 best3 = 83.4 (step 32: best3=83.4>best2=83.4)\n   - 最终 final = 82.45\n   - 问题: best3 (83.4) < best_value (84.9) < 粗调采样时的实际峰值 (84.82 at step 23)\n\n   根本原因: 0.2s APPROACH回退3步后，best2=83.4，但粗调时峰值是84.82。回退后反差反而下降了。然后0.1s FINE阶段也没能找到比best2更好的值。\n\n   问题分析:\n   - 样条峰值=84.9@pos=12.16，但粗调数据中pos=12对应的反差是84.82(step 23)\n   - 回退3步从pos=15回到pos=12，但实际反差只有82.43(step 26)\n   - 说明电机回退3步后没有回到之前的峰值位置——步长非线性问题仍然存在\n   - best3=83.4 等于 best2=83.4，条件是 `best3 > best2`，83.4 > 83.4 是False，不应该触发成功\n\n   等等，看step 32的日志: \"对焦成功(best3=83.4>best2=83.4)\"，但83.4不大于83.4。这是个bug!\n\n   让我看代码:\n   ```python\n   if self._best3_value > self._best2_value:\n   ```\n   \n   但日志显示 \"best3=83.4>best2=83.4\"。如果 best3 == best2，条件不满足。那为什么进入了DONE?\n\n   看step 31: \"精逼近(步2/10,best3=83.4,best2=83.4)\"\n   step 32: \"对焦成功(best3=83.4>best2=83.4)\"\n\n   等等，在step 31之后，step 32传入的contrast可能是83.44。在_step_fine中:\n   - _fine_step += 1 → 3\n   - contrast=83.44 > _best3_value(83.4)? 83.44 > 83.4 → True! _best3_value = 83.44\n   - _best3_value(83.44) > _best2_value(83.4)? 83.44 > 83.4 → True! → DONE\n\n   所以 best3=83.44 (四舍五入显示83.4)，best2=83.4。83.44 > 83.4 → True。但显示时都显示为83.4，所以看起来是相等的。\n\n   核心问题: 精调的 best3(83.44) 比粗调的 best_value(84.9) 还低。精调没有找到比粗调更好的结果。\n\n   原因: 0.2s回退3步后，电机位置已经偏离了真实峰值。0.1s精调在这个偏离的位置附近搜索，自然找不到比粗调峰值更好的值。\n\n   解决方案: 精调应该在粗调峰值附近搜索，而不是在回退后的位置搜索。但问题是，回退后的位置可能不是真实峰值（因为步长非线性）。\n\n2. **快门时间默认1/25**: 不再考虑快门时间，只考虑是否打开慢快门。慢快门在点击框选按钮时读取一次。\n\n3. **下拉菜单切换到局部对焦不再切换设备模式，在点击框选按钮时再切换**。\n\nLet me now plan the precise modifications:\n\n### 修改计划\n\n**修改1: 精调必须比粗调更好**\n- 问题: 0.2s回退后电机位置偏离真实峰值，0.1s精调在偏离位置搜索\n- 方案: 精调阶段如果10步内 best3 未超过 best2，不应该直接结束。而是应该扩大搜索范围。\n- 但用户说\"精调结果必须比粗调要更好\"，这意味着精调阶段必须找到比best2更高的反差值。\n- 实际上问题是: 回退3步后反差(82.43)比粗调峰值(84.82)还低。说明回退步数不对，或者步长非线性导致回退过头/不够。\n- 更根本的解决方案: best2应该是粗调阶段扫描时的_best_value(84.9)，而不是回退后的contrast(83.4)。\n- 这样精调只需要在当前位置附近微调，找到>=84.9的值即可。\n\nWait, let me re-read the user's requirement:\n\"当已经执行0.2s逼近，获取到best时，新增使用0.1s逼近。将现在0.2s逼近获取值定为best2。最终0.1s的逼近方法是先从0.2s方向移动，最多10步，如果趋势下降，则反向移动，必须得到最终焦点best3，best3必须大于best2\"\n\nSo the user wants:\n- best2 = the value after 0.2s approach completes\n- best3 = the value found during 0.1s fine approach, must be > best2\n\nThe problem is best2=83.4 but the scan peak was 84.82. The 0.2s approach didn't land at the peak.\n\nThe fix should be: best2 should be set to the scan peak value (_best_value), not the contrast at the end of approach. Or better: best2 should track the maximum contrast seen during the approach phase.\n\nLet me re-read the current code:\n```python\ndef _step_approach(self, contrast):\n    self._approach_remaining -= 1\n    if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n        # 0.2s 回退完成 → 记录 best2\n        self._best2_value = contrast  # ← 只记录最后一步的值\n        ...\n```\n\nThe issue is `self._best2_value = contrast` only records the last step's contrast, not the maximum during approach. It should track the max:\n\n```python\ndef _step_approach(self, contrast):\n    if contrast > self._best2_value:\n        self._best2_value = contrast\n    self._approach_remaining -= 1\n    ...\n```\n\nBut even this won't solve the fundamental problem: the approach didn't land at the peak. The scan peak was 84.82 at pos=12, but after 3 steps back, the contrast is only 82.43.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user's requirement is clear: \"精调结果必须比粗调要更好\"。This means best3 must be > best2. If best2 is the value at the end of approach (83.4), then best3 just needs to be > 83.4. But the user also expects the final result to be better than the scan peak (84.82).\n\nI think the real fix should be:\n1. best2 = max contrast during 0.2s approach (not just the last value)\n2. If best3 doesn't exceed best2 within 10 steps, continue searching (don't just stop)\n3. Or: if 10 steps aren't enough, expand the step or change direction\n\nBut the user said \"禁止过度开发\"，so I should make minimal changes.\n\nThe simplest fix: track best2 as the max during approach, and if FINE doesn't find best3 > best2 in 10 steps, don't return success - return the best value found.\n\nActually, looking at the log more carefully:\n- Step 26 (approach start): contrast=82.43, best2 should be 82.43\n- Step 27: contrast=82.81, best2 should be 82.81\n- Step 28: contrast=82.98, best2 should be 82.98\n- Step 29 (approach done): contrast=83.43, best2 should be 83.43\n\nSo best2=83.43 if we track max. But the scan peak was 84.82. The approach didn't get back to the peak.\n\nThe fundamental issue is the 0.2s approach is imprecise. The 0.1s fine should be able to find a better position. But 83.43 → 83.44 is barely an improvement.\n\nThe real problem might be that the motor is in the wrong position. The scan found peak at pos=12 (contrast=84.82), but after 3 steps back from pos=15, the contrast is only 82.43. This means the motor didn't actually return to the pos=12 position.\n\nFor the \"精调结果必须比粗调要更好\" requirement, I think the best approach is:\n1. best2 = _best_value (scan peak), not the approach end value\n2. FINE阶段必须在10步内找到 > best2 的值\n3. 如果10步内没找到，不返回成功\n\nWait, but the user said \"将现在0.2s逼近获取值定为best2\"。So best2 is explicitly the value obtained during/after 0.2s approach. Let me track the max during approach:\n\n```python\ndef _step_approach(self, contrast):\n    if contrast > self._best2_value:\n        self._best2_value = contrast\n    ...\n```\n\nAnd for FINE:\n- If 10 steps not enough, don't just return. Continue with more steps or change direction.\n- But user said \"最多10步\"。So 10 steps is the limit.\n\nOK, I think the key issue is:\n1. best2 should be the MAX during approach, not just the last value\n2. The FINE phase needs to be more effective - maybe start in the direction toward the scan peak\n\nActually, let me re-think. The user's test shows:\n- Scan peak: 84.82 (pos=12)\n- After 3 steps back: 82.43, 82.81, 82.98, 83.43\n- These are INCREASING, which means the motor is moving toward the peak but hasn't reached it yet\n- So the motor needs to go further! The 3 steps weren't enough.\n\nThe problem is that the approach steps (3) were calculated from the spline peak position (pos=12.16, current pos=15, delta=3). But due to step non-linearity, 3 steps of 0.2s didn't cover the full distance.\n\nFor FINE phase: the contrast is still increasing (82.43 → 82.81 → 82.98 → 83.43), so FINE should continue in the same direction. And it does! But 83.43 → 81.87 (step 30, direction=focus_far) → wait, that's wrong direction!\n\nLooking at step 29: fine focus_near (contrast=83.43)\nStep 30: fine focus_far (contrast=81.87) — direction reversed!\nStep 31: fine focus_near (contrast=83.02) — direction reversed again!\nStep 32: done (contrast=83.44)\n\nSo FINE reversed direction at step 30 because 81.87 < 83.43 (best3). Then reversed again at step 31 because 83.02 < 83.43. Then at step 32, 83.44 > 83.43 → success.\n\nThe problem: FINE is oscillating around 83.x and barely finding 83.44 > 83.43. The real peak (84.82) is never reached because FINE is too close to the approach end position, not the real peak.\n\n**Root cause**: best2 is set to the contrast at the end of approach (83.43), not the scan peak (84.82). FINE only needs to beat 83.43, not 84.82. So it \"succeeds\" with a terrible result.\n\n**Fix**: best2 should be the scan peak (_best_value), not the approach end contrast. This way FINE must find something better than 84.82 to succeed.\n\nBut wait, the user said \"将现在0.2s逼近获取值定为best2\". So best2 IS the value obtained during 0.2s approach. If I set best2 = _best_value (scan peak), that's not \"0.2s逼近获取值\".\n\nHmm, let me re-interpret: \"0.2s逼近获取值\" could mean \"the best value obtained during 0.2s approach\", which would be the max contrast during approach. Currently it's only the last step's contrast.\n\nIf I track max during approach:\n- Step 26: 82.43 → best2=82.43\n- Step 27: 82.81 → best2=82.81\n- Step 28: 82.98 → best2=82.98\n- Step 29: 83.43 → best2=83.43\n\nStill 83.43, which is less than scan peak 84.82.\n\nI think the real fix is: best2 should be the max of (scan peak, approach max). Because the scan peak IS the best value found so far, and approach is trying to get back to it. If approach doesn't reach it, best2 should still be the scan peak.\n\nActually, the simplest interpretation: best2 = max contrast seen so far (from scan + approach). This is _best_value (scan) updated with approach values.\n\nLet me just set: `self._best2_value = max(self._best_value, contrast)` when approach completes. And also track max during approach.\n\nActually, even simpler: `self._best2_value = self._best_value` at the start of approach, and update with `max` during approach. This way best2 = scan peak initially, and if approach finds something better, it updates.\n\nWait, but the user explicitly said \"0.2s逼近获取值定为best2\". I think they mean the value obtained from the 0.2s approach phase. The problem is this value (83.43) is worse than the scan peak (84.82).\n\nI think the user's intent is: best2 is the reference for FINE to beat. If best2 is set too low (83.43 instead of 84.82), FINE can \"succeed\" with a bad result. The user wants FINE to find something BETTER than what we've seen so far.\n\nSo the fix should be: best2 = max(_best_value, max contrast during approach). This ensures FINE must beat the scan peak.\n\nLet me now also address the other requirements:\n\n**修改2: 快门时间默认1/25**\n- region_base.py: `calc_stable_delay` 不再读取设备快门\n- 默认延迟 = 1/25 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.58s\n- 如果慢快门开启，读取慢快门倍率\n- 慢快门在点击框选按钮时读取一次\n\n**修改3: 框选时才切换设备模式**\n- console.html: `onFocusModeChange('local')` → 不调用 setFocusMode\n- index.html: `toggleRegionMode('focus')` → 点击框选时才 setFocusMode('area')\n\nWait, the user said:\n\"下拉菜单切换到局部对焦，不再把设备切换到手动对焦，而是在点击框选按钮时再切换\"\n\nSo:\n- onFocusModeChange('local') → 只显示 UI，不设置设备模式\n- toggleRegionMode('focus') → 点击框选时才 setFocusMode('area')\n\nAnd:\n\"慢快门在点击局部对焦的框选按钮的同时，读取一次数据\"\n\nSo when toggleRegionMode('focus') is called, also read slow shutter status once.\n\nLet me now list the modification plan:\n\n### 修改计划\n\n1. **autofocus.py - best2 跟踪 max**\n   - `_step_approach`: best2 = max(_best_value, contrast)，跟踪整个 approach 阶段的 max\n   - 这样 FINE 必须找到比扫描峰值更好的值\n\n2. **autofocus.py - FINE 未达标不返回成功**\n   - 如果10步内 best3 未超过 best2，不返回\"对焦成功\"，返回\"对焦完成(精逼近未达标)\"\n\n3. **region_base.py - 简化延迟计算**\n   - `calc_stable_delay`: 默认 1/25 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.58s\n   - 不再调用 `get_exposure_time`\n   - 如果慢快门开启，使用倍率\n   - 慢快门状态在框选时读取一次，传给 FocusSearcher\n\n4. **console.html - onFocusModeChange**\n   - 'local' 模式: 只显示 UI，不调用 setFocusMode\n\n5. **index.html - toggleRegionMode**\n   - 'focus' 模式: 点击框选时才 setFocusMode('area')\n   - 同时读取一次慢快门状态\n\nActually, wait. Let me re-read the user's requirement about slow shutter:\n\"现在，给我把所有的快门时间，都默认成1/25来计算，不再考虑快门时间，只考虑是否已经打开慢快门。慢快门在点击局部对焦的框选按钮的同时，读取一次数据。\"\n\nSo:\n- 快门时间固定为 1/25 (0.04s)\n- 不再从设备读取快门时间\n- 只需要知道慢快门是否开启\n- 慢快门状态在点击框选按钮时读取一次\n\nThis means:\n- `calc_stable_delay` 不再从设备读取快门\n- 默认延迟 = 0.04 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.58s\n- 如果慢快门开启，延迟 = 慢快门倍率 * 0.04 * 2 + 0.5\n- 慢快门倍率在框选时读取一次\n\nBut `calc_stable_delay` currently takes `client` as parameter and reads from device. If we change it to not read from device, we need to change the signature.\n\nActually, the simplest approach:\n- `calc_stable_delay` 固定返回 0.58s (1/25 * 2 + 0.5)\n- 如果慢快门开启，使用慢快门倍率\n- 慢快门倍率通过参数传入\n\nWait, but the user said \"慢快门在点击局部对焦的框选按钮的同时，读取一次数据\"。这意味着慢快门状态是在框选时读取的，然后传给对焦算法。\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The current flow:\n1. toggleRegionMode('focus') → _finishRegion() → POST /api/v1/vision/focus-search\n2. FocusSearcher.run() → calc_stable_delay(client) reads from device each time\n\nThe new flow:\n1. toggleRegionMode('focus') → read slow shutter status → pass to focus-search API\n2. FocusSearcher.run() → use the pre-read slow shutter status\n\nBut this requires changing the API endpoint to accept slow shutter status. That's too much change.\n\nSimpler approach:\n- FocusSearcher reads slow shutter once at the start of run()\n- calc_stable_delay takes the slow shutter ratio as parameter, not client\n\nOr even simpler:\n- calc_stable_delay always returns 0.58s (1/25 * 2 + 0.5)\n- If slow shutter is on, it returns 0.58s * slow_ratio\n- FocusSearcher reads slow shutter once at start, then uses fixed delay\n\nLet me think about the simplest change that satisfies the user's requirement:\n\n1. `calc_stable_delay` no longer reads from device\n2. It takes a `slow_ratio` parameter (default 1.0)\n3. Returns `0.04 * 2 * slow_ratio + 0.5`\n4. FocusSearcher reads slow shutter once at start, calculates slow_ratio, then passes to calc_stable_delay\n\nBut wait, `calc_stable_delay` is also used by whitebalance.py. Let me check:\n\nActually, looking at the code, `calc_stable_delay` is imported in both autofocus.py and whitebalance.py. If I change its signature, I need to update both.\n\nThe user said \"禁止过度开发\"，so I should minimize changes. Let me just:\n1. Change `calc_stable_delay` to use fixed 1/25 instead of reading from device\n2. Keep the slow shutter check (read from device once)\n3. The signature stays the same (takes client), but internally it reads slow shutter status differently\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's requirement again:\n\"现在，给我把所有的快门时间，都默认成1/25来计算，不再考虑快门时间，只考虑是否已经打开慢快门。\"\n\nThis means:\n- 快门时间 = 1/25 (固定)\n- 不再读取 ShutterLevel\n- 只检查慢快门是否开启\n\nSo `get_exposure_time` should:\n- 不再读取 ShutterLevel\n- 只检查 minShutterLevelLimit != maxShutterLevelLimit\n- 如果慢快门关闭: 返回 1/25 = 0.04s\n- 如果慢快门开启: 返回 1/25 * slow_ratio\n\nAnd `calc_stable_delay`:\n- delay = 0.04 * 2 * slow_ratio + 0.5\n- 如果慢快门关闭: delay = 0.58s\n- 如果慢快门开启: delay = 0.58s * slow_ratio (approximately)\n\nBut the user also said \"慢快门在点击局部对焦的框选按钮的同时，读取一次数据\"。这意味着不应该在每次 calc_stable_delay 时都读取设备，而是提前读取一次。\n\nOK, let me plan this more carefully:\n\n1. `region_base.py`:\n   - `get_exposure_time(client)`: 不再读取 ShutterLevel，只检查慢快门是否开启\n   - 如果慢快门关闭: 返回 0.04 (1/25)\n   - 如果慢快门开启: 返回 0.04 * slow_ratio\n   - `calc_stable_delay(client)`: 调用 get_exposure_time，返回 exposure * 2 + 0.5\n\n2. `autofocus.py` FocusSearcher.run():\n   - 开始时读取一次慢快门状态\n   - 后续使用固定延迟\n\nActually, the simplest approach that satisfies the user:\n- `get_exposure_time` 不再读取 ShutterLevel，只读取 minShutterLevelLimit 和 maxShutterLevelLimit 来判断慢快门\n- 如果 min == max (慢快门关闭): 返回 0.04\n- 如果 min != max (慢快门开启): 返回 0.04 * (max_time / 0.04) = max_time... 不对\n\nActually the user said \"默认成1/25来计算\"，所以基础快门固定为1/25。慢快门开启时，实际曝光 = 1/25 * 慢快门倍率。\n\n但慢快门倍率怎么算？如果不再读取 ShutterLevel，只读取 min/max limit：\n- min = \"1/25\", max = \"1/1\" → 倍率 = (1/1) / (1/25) = 25\n- 实际曝光 = 1/25 * 25 = 1s\n\nHmm, but the user said \"只考虑是否已经打开慢快门\"，不一定要计算倍率。可能只需要知道开关状态。\n\n如果慢快门关闭: delay = 0.04 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.58s\n如果慢快门开启: delay = ? \n\n用户说\"默认成1/25来计算\"，可能意思是无论慢快门是否开启，都用1/25来计算延迟。但这样如果慢快门开启（曝光时间可能是1秒），延迟只有0.58秒就不够了。\n\n我觉得用户的意思是：不再读取复杂的快门参数，简化为1/25。如果慢快门开启，就乘以倍率。倍率从 min/max limit 计算。\n\nOK let me just list the plan clearly and ask for confirmation. Actually, the user said \"列出修改计划\"，so I should just list the plan.\n\nLet me organize:\n\n### 问题分析\n\n**问题1: 精调结果比粗调差**\n```\n扫描峰值: 84.82 (pos=12)\n回退3步后: 82.43 → 82.81 → 82.98 → 83.43 (best2)\n精调结果: 83.44 (best3)\n83.44 < 84.82 → 精调比粗调差\n\n根因: best2 只记录了回退结束时的 contrast(83.43)，而不是扫描峰值(84.82)\n      FINE 只需要超过 83.43 就\"成功\"，门槛太低\n```\n\n**问题2: 快门时间计算过于复杂**\n```\n当前: 每步都 GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter → 读取 ShutterLevel + min/max\n要求: 默认 1/25，只检查慢快门开关，框选时读取一次\n```\n\n**问题3: 模式切换时机**\n```\n当前: onChange('local') → setFocusMode('area')\n要求: onChange('local') → 只显示UI\n      点击框选 → setFocusMode('area') + 读取慢快门\n```\n\n### 修改计划\n\n1. **autofocus.py - best2 改为扫描峰值**\n   - `_step_approach` 开始时: `self._best2_value = self._best_value` (扫描峰值)\n   - approach 阶段继续跟踪 max: `if contrast > self._best2_value: self._best2_value = contrast`\n   - 这样 FINE 必须找到 > 84.82 才能成功\n\n2. **autofocus.py - FINE 未达标时扩大搜索**\n   - 10步内未超过 best2 → 不返回\"成功\"，返回\"完成(未达标)\"\n   - 或者: 增加更多步数\n\n3. **region_base.py - 简化延迟计算**\n   - `get_exposure_time`: 不再读 ShutterLevel，只读 min/max limit\n   - 基础曝光 = 0.04 (1/25)\n   - 慢快门开启: 实际曝光 = 0.04 * slow_ratio\n   - `calc_stable_delay`: exposure * 2 + 0.5\n\n4. **console.html - onFocusModeChange**\n   - 'local': 只显示 UI，不调用 setFocusMode\n\n5. **index.html - toggleRegionMode**\n   - 'focus': 点击框选时才 setFocusMode('area')\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The user said \"禁止过度开发，精确修改\"。Let me minimize changes.\n\nFor the slow shutter, the simplest change:\n- `get_exposure_time`: 基础时间 = 0.04 (1/25)，不再读 ShutterLevel\n- 只读 min/max limit 判断慢快门\n- 如果慢快门开启: 0.04 * (max_time / min_time) ... 不，这太复杂了\n\n用户说\"只考虑是否已经打开慢快门\"。可能意思是：\n- 慢快门关闭: delay = 0.04 * 2 + 0.5 = 0.58s\n- 慢快门开启: delay = 更长（但怎么算？）\n\n我觉得用户的意思可能是：不再动态读取快门时间，固定用1/25。如果慢快门开启，就在框选时读取一次倍率。后续都用这个固定倍率。\n\n但这需要把倍率传给 FocusSearcher，然后 FocusSearcher 在每次 calc_stable_delay 时使用这个倍率。这需要修改 FocusSearcher 和 calc_stable_delay 的接口。\n\n太复杂了。让我简化：\n- `get_exposure_time`: 基础 = 0.04，如果慢快门开启，读取 max limit 计算倍率\n- `calc_stable_delay`: 调用 get_exposure_time，返回 delay\n- 不改变接口\n\n这样改动最小。只是 `get_exposure_time` 不再读取 ShutterLevel，改用固定 0.04。\n\nOK let me finalize the plan and present it to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 问题分析\n\n**问题1: 精调结果比粗调差**\n\n```\n扫描峰值: 84.82 (pos=12, step 23)\n回退3步:  82.43 → 82.81 → 82.98 → 83.43 (best2=83.43)\n精调结果: 83.44 (best3=83.44 > best2=83.43 → \"成功\")\n\n83.44 << 84.82 → 精调远低于粗调峰值\n\n根因: best2 = 回退结束时的 contrast(83.43)\n      不是扫描峰值(84.82)\n      FINE 只需超过 83.43 就\"成功\"，门槛太低\n```\n\n**问题2: 快门时间计算**\n\n```\n当前: 每步 GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter → 读 ShutterLevel + min/max\n要求: 默认 1/25，只检查慢快门开关，框选时读取一次\n```\n\n**问题3: 模式切换时机**\n\n```\n当前: onChange('local') → setFocusMode('area')\n要求: onChange('local') → 只显示UI\n      点击框选 → setFocusMode('area')\n```\n\n## 修改计划（5处精确修改）\n\n| # | 文件 | 修改 | 说明 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | autofocus.py | `_step_approach` 中 best2 初始化 | `self._best2_value = self._best_value`（扫描峰值），approach 中继续 `max` 跟踪。FINE 必须超过扫描峰值才能成功 |\n| 2 | autofocus.py | FINE 10步未达标 | 不返回\"成功\"，返回最大值 + \"未达标\"提示 |\n| 3 | region_base.py | `get_exposure_time` | 基础时间固定 0.04(1/25)，不再读 ShutterLevel，只读 min/max limit 判断慢快门是否开启 |\n| 4 | console.html | `onFocusModeChange('local')` | 只显示 UI，不调用 `setFocusMode` |\n| 5 | index.html | `toggleRegionMode('focus')` | 恢复点击框选时 `setFocusMode('area')` |\n\n**不修改**: FocusSearcher.run()、router.py、whitebalance.py\n\n需要确认后执行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":178335,"output":6723,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185058,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783370349182,"responseId":"cht000d2c8b@dx19f3929b8ed29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4232499","parentId":"5441c7b7","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:43:57.533Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47702\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 04:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n执行"}],"timestamp":1783370637527}}
{"type":"message","id":"fccd1fdd","parentId":"e4232499","timestamp":"2026-07-06T20:44:22.167Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_256096a5461f48ea8c0690b2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def _step_approach(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"逐步回退到峰值位置（每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）。\"\"\"\n        # best2 = 扫描峰值，approach 阶段继续跟踪 max\n        if contrast > self._best2_value:\n            self._best2_value = contrast\n\n        self._approach_remaining -= 1\n\n        if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n            # 0.2s 回退完成 → 进入 0.1s 精逼近\n            # best2 = max(扫描峰值, approach阶段最大值)\n            self._best3_value = self._best2_value\n            self._fine_step = 0\n            self._fine_dir = self._approach_dir  # 继续同方向\n            self._state = self.FINE\n            action = \"focus_near\" if self._fine_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n            return {\n                \"action\": action,\n                \"duration\": 0.1,\n                \"stage\": \"fine\",\n                \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"粗逼近完成(best2={self._best2_value:.1f}),开始精逼近(0.1s)\"\n            }\n\n        # 继续回退\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"duration\": 0.2,\n            \"stage\": \"approach\",\n            \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"逼近(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步,峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\"\n        }","oldText":"    def _step_approach(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"逐步回退到峰值位置（每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）。\"\"\"\n        self._approach_remaining -= 1\n\n        if self._approach_remaining <= 0:\n            # 0.2s 回退完成 → 记录 best2，进入 0.1s 精逼近\n            self._best2_value = contrast\n            self._best3_value = contrast\n            self._fine_step = 0\n            self._fine_dir = self._approach_dir  # 继续同方向\n            self._state = self.FINE\n            action = \"focus_near\" if self._fine_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n            return {\n                \"action\": action,\n                \"duration\": 0.1,\n                \"stage\": \"fine\",\n                \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"粗逼近完成(best2={self._best2_value:.1f}),开始精逼近(0.1s)\"\n            }\n\n        # 继续回退\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._approach_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"duration\": 0.2,\n            \"stage\": \"approach\",\n            \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"逼近(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步,峰值={self._best_value:.1f})\"\n        }"},{"newText":"        # 达到最大步数\n        if self._fine_step >= self._fine_max_steps:\n            # best3 未超过 best2，取最大值\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            best = max(self._best3_value, self._best2_value)\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦完成(精逼近{self._fine_step}步,best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f},未达标)\",\n                \"best\": best\n            }","oldText":"        # 达到最大步数\n        if self._fine_step >= self._fine_max_steps:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            best = max(self._best3_value, self._best2_value)\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦完成(精逼近{self._fine_step}步,best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": best\n            }"},{"newText":"        # best2 初始化为扫描峰值\n        self._best2_value = 0.0   # approach 阶段初始化为 _best_value\n        self._best3_value = 0.0   # 0.1s 精逼近的 best","oldText":"        # 精逼近 (0.1s)\n        self._best2_value = 0.0   # 0.2s 回退完成后的 best\n        self._best3_value = 0.0   # 0.1s 精逼近的 best"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":185212,"output":1240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":186452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783370637534,"responseId":"cht000de590@dx19f392c76fe29bb503"}}
