{"type":"message","id":"a7d0b578","parentId":"b7416c8a","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:11:11.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改完成。\n\n## 修改报告\n\n```\n文件: autofocus.py (3处修改)\n```\n\n| # | 修改 | 说明 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 新增趋势下降检测 | `_step_count >= 8` 时检查最近8步后半均值 < 前半 × 0.9 → 反向。放在 `decline_after_best >= 8` **之前**，优先触发 |\n| 2 | 新增 `decline_after_best >= 8` 反向 | 连续8步无新 best → 反向（不限 best 值）。之前的 `decline_after_best >= 3 AND best > 50` 在 best ≤ 50 时永远不触发 |\n| 3 | 新增 `_check_declining_trend()` 方法 | 取最近8步，前4步均值 vs 后4步均值，下降 > 10% → 趋势下降 |\n\n### 老板测试数据验证\n\n```\nattempt 3 数据:\n  pos 0-2: 37→39→41 (上升, best=41.3)\n  pos 3-9: 40→38→39→35→37→33→28 (波动下降)\n  \n  pos 9 (28.28): 趋势检测触发\n    first_half avg = 40.00\n    second_half avg = 33.90\n    33.90 < 40.00 × 0.9 = 36.0 → 趋势下降!\n    \n  但 attempt=3 → _do_retry() 返回 False → FAILED\n  (3次重试已耗尽，这是正确行为)\n```\n\n趋势检测已生效。这个场景失败是因为3次重试都方向错误，反差全程 ≤ 44（低于阈值50），场景本身不适合对焦。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":206379,"output":389,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":206768,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783372242824,"responseId":"cht000d5408@dx19f3945275229bb503"}}
