{"type":"message","id":"1e91bad1","parentId":"e963d326","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:32:14.938Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8434325b0b6d49e9936aea1e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            if self._interrupted:\r\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\r\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'interrupt', 'message': '用户停止'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n                break\r\n\r\n            contrast = calc_contrast(bgr)\r\n            cmd = af.step(contrast)\r\n            step_count += 1\r\n\r\n            event = {\r\n                \"type\": \"focus\",\r\n                \"step\": step_count,\r\n                \"stage\": cmd.get(\"stage\", \"\"),\r\n                \"action\": cmd[\"action\"],\r\n                \"contrast\": cmd[\"contrast\"],\r\n                \"duration\": cmd[\"duration\"],\r\n                \"message\": cmd[\"message\"]\r\n            }\r\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps(event)}\\n\\n\"\r\n\r\n            if cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":\r\n                # 验证\r\n                bgr2, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\r\n                final_contrast = calc_contrast(bgr2) if bgr2 is not None else cmd[\"contrast\"]\r\n                best = cmd.get(\"best\", cmd[\"contrast\"])\r\n                verified = final_contrast >= best * 0.95\r\n\r\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'done', 'final_contrast': round(final_contrast, 2), 'best_contrast': round(best, 2), 'total_steps': step_count, 'verified': verified})}\\n\\n\"\r\n                break\r\n\r\n            # 移动\r\n            await asyncio.to_thread(self._move_focus, cmd[\"action\"], cmd[\"duration\"])\r\n            await asyncio.sleep(cmd[\"duration\"])\r\n            await asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\r\n            delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\r\n            await asyncio.sleep(delay)  # 等待稳定\r\n\r\n            # 重新截图\r\n            bgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\r\n            if bgr is None:\r\n\n[7 more lines in file. Use offset=750 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783373534938}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ba56dff","parentId":"1e91bad1","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:32:30.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"流程检查完毕。当前流程：\n\n```\n① contrast = calc_contrast(bgr)     ← 计算上一步截图的反差\n② cmd = af.step(contrast)           ← 算法决策\n③ yield SSE event\n④ if stop → 验证截图 → break\n⑤ _move_focus(action, duration)     ← 发送移动指令\n⑥ sleep(duration)                   ← 等待移动完成\n⑦ _stop_focus()                     ← 停止电机\n⑧ calc_stable_delay()               ← 计算延迟\n⑨ sleep(delay)                      ← 等待稳定\n⑩ _capture()                        ← 截图\n⑪ if bgr is None → error → break\n⑫ 回到 ①\n```\n\n**流程是正确的**：移动 → 等待 → 停止 → 等待稳定 → 截图。截图时电机已经停止。\n\n**但问题在第⑥步**：`sleep(duration)` 只等待了 duration 时间（0.1s 或 0.2s），但 `_move_focus` 发送的是 ISAPI 指令，指令发送后电机才开始响应。如果网络延迟 + ISAPI 响应时间 > 0，实际电机运动时间 < duration。\n\n**更关键的问题**：`_move_focus` 内部调用 `self.mgr.ptz_move()`，这是一个**非阻塞**指令 — 它只发送 ISAPI 请求，不等待电机实际开始运动。所以：\n\n```\n实际时序:\n  t=0:    发送 ptz_move 指令\n  t=0.1:  ISAPI 响应返回（网络延迟）\n  t=0.1:  电机开始运动\n  t=0.3:  sleep(0.2) 结束 → 发送 stop 指令\n  t=0.4:  stop 指令到达电机 → 电机开始减速\n  t=0.5:  电机完全停止\n  t=0.5:  sleep(delay) 等待稳定\n  t=1.6:  截图\n```\n\n**如果网络延迟较大，电机可能在 sleep(duration) 期间还没开始运动，运动时间很短就收到了 stop 指令。** 但这不会导致\"截图时电机还在动\"。\n\n**截图失败的真正原因**：不是电机问题，而是 `_capture()` 函数内部超时或设备无响应。让我检查 `_capture` 的实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2bf167d91c3345af9dc544f3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\api\\router.py -Pattern \"capture_func|def.*capture\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Select-Object -First 20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":216822,"output":598,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":217420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783373534943,"responseId":"cht000d7f47@dx19f39589eab29c2503"}}
