{"type":"message","id":"5db1c560","parentId":"90c68e6b","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:35:29.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改完成。\n\n## 检查报告\n\n### 当前流程\n\n```\n① _move_focus()     → 发送移动指令\n② sleep(duration)    → 等待移动(0.1s/0.2s)\n③ _stop_focus()      → 停止电机\n④ calc_stable_delay  → 计算延迟(1.08s)\n⑤ sleep(delay)       → 等待稳定\n⑥ _capture()         → 截图\n⑦ 截图失败 → break\n```\n\n**流程正确**：截图时电机已停止，且有1.08s稳定等待。\n\n### 修复内容\n\n```\n修复前: 截图失败 → 直接 break（电机可能未停）\n修复后: 截图失败 → _stop_focus() → break\n```\n\n### 截图失败根因分析\n\n不是电机问题（电机在步骤③已停止）。截图失败更可能是：\n- ISAPI 截图请求超时\n- 设备无响应\n- 网络问题\n\n需要实测观察是否还出现截图失败。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":223799,"output":231,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":224030,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783373717867,"responseId":"cht000d3191@dx19f395b703d2872503"}}
