{"type":"message","id":"e4bda3c6","parentId":"f4fc0e3d","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:43:10.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check if there are overly frequent commands that might be causing the screenshot failures. This is a good question - if we're sending too many ISAPI commands in quick succession, we might be overwhelming the device or causing network issues.\n\nLet me think about the current flow:\n1. Move focus (ISAPI command)\n2. Sleep for duration\n3. Stop focus (ISAPI command)\n4. Calculate stable delay\n5. Sleep for delay\n6. Capture screenshot (ISAPI command)\n7. Loop back to step 1\n\nThe concern is: are we sending commands too frequently without enough delay between them?\n\nLooking at the current implementation:\n- We send move_focus command\n- Wait for duration (0.1s or 0.2s)\n- Send stop_focus command\n- Calculate delay (which includes 1.0s base delay)\n- Wait for delay\n- Capture screenshot\n\nThe total time between commands should be:\n- After stop_focus: wait delay (1.08s minimum)\n- Then capture\n- Then loop back to move_focus\n\nSo the minimum time between consecutive ISAPI commands should be around 1.08s, which seems reasonable.\n\nHowever, I should check:\n1. Are there any other frequent commands being sent?\n2. Is the delay calculation actually sufficient?\n3. Are there any race conditions or concurrent operations?\n\nLet me read the current implementation to check for any issues.\n\nI need to check:\n1. The FocusSearcher.run() method to see the command flow\n2. The calc_stable_delay implementation\n3. Any other places where ISAPI commands might be sent frequently\n\nActually, I should also check if there's any rate limiting or throttling mechanism in place. The device might have a maximum command rate that we're exceeding.\n\nLet me start by reading the current FocusSearcher implementation to understand the flow better.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9d75829e57be48e8b4674dd2","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":750,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":717,"output":487,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":246567,"totalTokens":247771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783374156011,"responseId":"msg_54e124ef-0e5c-4182-90b8-95738b1cb26f"}}
