{"type":"message","id":"0af93f89","parentId":"65e7ad0e","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:44:15.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d9811c6dee4c49c38a3216de","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def _capture_and_crop(client, mgr, device_ip: str, category: str,\r\n                      x: float, y: float, w: float, h: float) -> tuple:\r\n    \"\"\"ISAPI 截图 → 按比例裁剪 → 返回 (bgr, 截图路径, 裁剪信息dict)。\r\n\r\n    统一入口，白平衡和对焦共用。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import time as _time\r\n    from src.controlpanel.region_base import calc_stable_delay\r\n    delay = calc_stable_delay(client)\r\n    _time.sleep(delay)  # v8.44: 统一延时\r\n    jpg = client.capture_picture()\r\n    if not jpg:\r\n        return None, \"\", {\"error\": \"ISAPI截图失败\"}\r\n\r\n    # 保存全图\r\n    ts = int(_time.time() * 1000)\r\n    temp_dir = _temp_dir(category, device_ip)\r\n    full_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"full_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n    with open(full_path, \"wb\") as f:\r\n        f.write(jpg)\r\n\r\n    bgr = cv2.imdecode(np.frombuffer(jpg, np.uint8), cv2.IMREAD_COLOR)\r\n    if bgr is None:\r\n        return None, full_path, {\"error\": \"图像解码失败\"}\r\n\r\n    full_h, full_w = bgr.shape[:2]\r\n\r\n    # 裁剪\r\n    if w > 0 and h > 0:\r\n        x1 = max(0, int(x * full_w))\r\n        y1 = max(0, int(y * full_h))\r\n        x2 = min(full_w, int((x + w) * full_w))\r\n        y2 = min(full_h, int((y + h) * full_h))\r\n        if x2 <= x1 or y2 <= y1:\r\n            return bgr, full_path, {\"error\": \"裁剪区域无效\"}\r\n        cropped = bgr[y1:y2, x1:x2]\r\n        crop_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"crop_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n        cv2.imwrite(crop_path, cropped)\r\n    else:\r\n        cropped = bgr\r\n\n[276 more lines in file. Use offset=4044 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783374255071}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2d348a6","parentId":"0af93f89","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:44:36.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check if there are overly frequent ISAPI requests that might cause screenshot failures. Let me analyze the request frequency per loop iteration.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到关键问题了！`_capture_and_crop` 函数内部**又调用了一次** `calc_stable_delay` 并 sleep。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_de5f7341698f499b8f87e47f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"\n# 统计每步循环的ISAPI请求\nprint('=== 每步循环 ISAPI 请求统计 ===')\nprint()\nprint('1. _move_focus()     → ptz_move()     → 1次 HTTP PUT')\nprint('2. sleep(duration)   → 等待 0.1~0.2s')\nprint('3. _stop_focus()     → ptz_stop()     → 1次 HTTP PUT')\nprint('4. calc_stable_delay → GET /Shutter   → 1次 HTTP GET (读取慢快门)')\nprint('5. sleep(delay)      → 等待 1.08s')\nprint('6. _capture()        → _capture_and_crop():')\nprint('   6a. calc_stable_delay → GET /Shutter → 1次 HTTP GET (重复!)')\nprint('   6b. sleep(delay)      → 再等 1.08s (重复!)')\nprint('   6c. capture_picture   → 1次 HTTP GET (实际截图)')\nprint()\nprint('总计: 5次 HTTP 请求/步')\nprint('总等待: 0.2s + 1.08s + 1.08s = 2.36s/步')\nprint()\nprint('=== 问题 ===')\nprint('calc_stable_delay + sleep 被调用了两次!')\nprint('FocusSearcher.run() 调一次, _capture_and_crop() 又调一次')\nprint('每步多等 1.08s, 多发送 1次 GET /Shutter')\nprint()\nprint('=== 对比老板数据 ===')\nprint('29步 x 2.36s = 68.4s')\nprint('老板日志: 04:34:55 ~ 04:35:51 = 56s')\nprint('29步 x 56/29 = 1.93s/步')\nprint('差异: 1.08s (正好是一次多余的 delay)')\n\"\n","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":808,"output":593,"cacheRead":246567,"cacheWrite":2713,"totalTokens":250681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783374255078,"responseId":"msg_992d9cda-31c5-485d-b2f0-30d4d2e5da01"}}
