{"type":"message","id":"9dbe3cf3","parentId":"1168b999","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:45:28.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改完成。\n\n## 检查报告\n\n### 发现的问题\n\n```\n每步循环 ISAPI 请求:\n  ① ptz_move()          → 1次 HTTP PUT (移动)\n  ② sleep(duration)     → 等待 0.1~0.2s\n  ③ ptz_stop()          → 1次 HTTP PUT (停止)\n  ④ calc_stable_delay   → 1次 HTTP GET (读Shutter) ← 第1次\n  ⑤ sleep(1.08s)        → 等待稳定\n  ⑥ _capture_and_crop():\n     ⑥a calc_stable_delay → 1次 HTTP GET (读Shutter) ← 第2次！重复!\n     ⑥b sleep(1.08s)      → 等待稳定 ← 重复!\n     ⑥c capture_picture   → 1次 HTTP GET (截图)\n\n修复前: 5次 HTTP 请求/步，2.36s/步\n修复后: 4次 HTTP 请求/步，1.28s/步\n```\n\n### 修复\n\n```\n文件: router.py _capture_and_crop()\n删除: calc_stable_delay(client) + sleep(delay)（调用方已等待）\n```\n\n### 效果\n\n- 每步减少 1次 HTTP GET 请求（少读一次 Shutter）\n- 每步减少 1.08s 等待时间\n- 降低设备 ISAPI 请求频率，减少截图超时风险"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":228230,"output":327,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":228557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783374314404,"responseId":"cht000d7bdf@dx19f39648c662871503"}}
