{"type":"message","id":"cf0e9454","parentId":"ce73c0d3","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:46:39.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已回滚。\n\n## 当前实际等待时间\n\n```\n每步循环:\n  ① _move_focus()          → 发送移动指令\n  ② sleep(duration)         → 0.1~0.2s\n  ③ _stop_focus()           → 停止电机\n  ④ calc_stable_delay()     → 1.08s (FocusSearcher中)\n  ⑤ sleep(1.08s)            → 等待\n  ⑥ _capture_and_crop():\n     ⑥a calc_stable_delay() → 1.08s (重复)\n     ⑥b sleep(1.08s)        → 等待\n     ⑥c capture_picture()   → 截图\n\n电机停止后总等待 = 1.08 + 1.08 = 2.16s\n```\n\n之前我把 `BASE_STABLE_DELAY` 从 0.5 改到 1.0，所以：\n- 修改前: 0.58 + 0.58 = 1.16s\n- 修改后: 1.08 + 1.08 = 2.16s\n\n2.16s 应该足够。问题是每步多 1 次 HTTP GET（读 Shutter）。\n\n要保留 2.16s 等待但消除重复 HTTP 请求，可以：删除 FocusSearcher 中的 `calc_stable_delay + sleep`，只靠 `_capture_and_crop` 内部的那一次。这样等待还是 1.08s，但只有 1 次 HTTP GET。\n\n或者：把 `calc_stable_delay` 的结果缓存，不重复读取设备。\n\n老板指示怎么做？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":229913,"output":358,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":230271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783374386887,"responseId":"cht000d9609@dx19f3965a0ba2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3ad607b","parentId":"cf0e9454","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:47:40.467Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47755\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 05:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n？？？？你在说什么东西？扯淡玩意儿！我要求等待固定1s+动态1/25*慢快门（如果有）\n你一会儿1.08，一会儿2.16，还有0.58，都是什么飞机啊？！"}],"timestamp":1783374460461}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3d1259b","parentId":"e3ad607b","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:48:28.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求很明确：\n1. 固定等待1s\n2. 如果慢快门开启，加上动态的 1/25 * 慢快门倍率\n\n现在代码里 `calc_stable_delay` 被调用了两次（FocusSearcher和_capture_and_crop），导致重复等待和重复HTTP请求。\n\n正确的修复：\n1. `calc_stable_delay` 应该只返回 1.0 + (慢快门额外时间)\n2. 只调用一次，不能重复\n\n让我理清：\n- BASE_STABLE_DELAY 现在是 1.0s\n- `calc_stable_delay` = exposure * 2 + BASE_STABLE_DELAY = 0.04 * 2 + 1.0 = 1.08s\n\n但老板要的是：固定1s + 慢快门时间。不是 exposure * 2 + 1.0。\n\n老板要求的公式：\n- 无慢快门: delay = 1.0s\n- 有慢快门: delay = 1.0 + 1/25 * slow_ratio\n\n所以 `calc_stable_delay` 应该改成：\n- BASE_STABLE_DELAY = 1.0\n- 无慢快门: 返回 1.0\n- 有慢快门: 返回 1.0 + 0.04 * slow_ratio\n\n而且只调用一次。删除 FocusSearcher 或 _capture_and_crop 中的重复调用。\n\n让我选择删除哪个：\n- _capture_and_crop 是公共函数，白平衡也用。删除它内部的 delay 会影响白平衡。\n- FocusSearcher.run() 是对焦专用的。\n\n最安全的方案：保留 _capture_and_crop 内部的 delay（因为白平衡也需要），删除 FocusSearcher.run() 中的重复调用。\n\n但这样白平衡也会有两次 delay... 让我检查白平衡的调用路径。\n\n实际上，让我重新看代码。FocusSearcher.run() 的流程是：\n1. move_focus\n2. sleep(duration)\n3. stop_focus\n4. calc_stable_delay → 1.08s\n5. sleep(delay)\n6. _capture → _capture_and_crop → calc_stable_delay → 1.08s → sleep → capture\n\n所以确实是两次 delay。\n\n修复方案：\n1. 修改 calc_stable_delay 公式为：固定1s + 慢快门时间\n2. 删除 FocusSearcher.run() 中的 calc_stable_delay + sleep（只靠 _capture_and_crop 内部的那次）\n\n这样每步只有1次 delay，公式是：1.0 + slow_shutter_extra\n\n让我执行。\n收到。修复：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5a12377146b94c149873f2c5","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门额外曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门 1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门是否开启。\n    返回慢快门额外时间（无慢快门返回0）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return 0.0\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                return max_time - min_time\n\n        return 0.0\n    except Exception:\n        return 0.0","oldText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取实际曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门固定 1/25=0.04s。只检查慢快门是否开启。\n    \"\"\"\n    default = 0.04  # 1/25s\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return default\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                slow_ratio = max_time / default\n                return default * slow_ratio\n\n        return default\n    except Exception:\n        return default"},{"newText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    公式: 固定1s + 1/25 × 慢快门倍率（如果有）\n    \"\"\"\n    slow_extra = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return 1.0 + slow_extra","oldText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    延时 = 曝光时间 × 2 + 基础延迟(1.0s)\n    \"\"\"\n    exposure = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return exposure * 2 + BASE_STABLE_DELAY"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":2088,"output":1465,"cacheRead":249442,"cacheWrite":2731,"totalTokens":255726,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783374460468,"responseId":"msg_4a800804-f996-4626-a7cb-08aa050b9c39"}}
