{"type":"message","id":"226db0d7","parentId":"0d6ed419","timestamp":"2026-07-06T21:51:37.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在状态清楚了：\n\n- `region_base.py`: `calc_stable_delay` = 1.0 + 慢快门额外时间 ✅\n- `_capture_and_crop`: 内部调用 `calc_stable_delay` + sleep ✅（白平衡和对焦共用）\n- `FocusSearcher.run()`: 已删除重复的 `calc_stable_delay + sleep` ✅\n\n当前流程已经正确：延迟只在 `_capture_and_crop` 内部执行一次。FocusSearcher 不再重复调用。\n\n但 `calc_stable_delay` 每次都调用 `get_exposure_time` → 发送 HTTP GET `/Image/channels/1/Shutter`。每步截图都会读一次设备。这不是\"无意义的错误设备请求\"——这是为了检测慢快门状态。\n\n但老板说\"删掉无意义的错误的设备请求\"。如果慢快门状态在一次对焦过程中不会变化，可以在开始时读一次，后续复用。但这需要改接口，可能过度开发。\n\n当前状态已经是正确的：**每步只有1次延迟调用（在 `_capture_and_crop` 内部），1次 HTTP GET Shutter**。\n\n修改完成。当前状态：\n\n```\n每步流程:\n  ① _move_focus()                    → 1次 HTTP PUT\n  ② sleep(duration)                   → 等待 0.1~0.2s\n  ③ _stop_focus()                     → 1次 HTTP PUT\n  ④ _capture() → _capture_and_crop():\n     ④a calc_stable_delay(client)     → 1次 HTTP GET (读Shutter)\n     ④b sleep(1.0 + 慢快门)           → 等待\n     ④c capture_picture()             → 1次 HTTP GET (截图)\n\n总HTTP请求: 4次/步\n总等待: 0.2s + 1.0s(+慢快门) = 1.2s/步\n无重复延迟 ✅\n```\n\n`region_base.py` 的 `calc_stable_delay` 保持不变，白平衡和对焦共用。FocusSearcher 不再重复调用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":235448,"output":454,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":235902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783374681681,"responseId":"cht000d93b9@dx19f396a24ef2872503"}}
