{"type":"message","id":"a8ef4fb4","parentId":"1e3c5c7e","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:02:18.090Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_97b5781c7d224fe0a1bf4726","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \"\"\"精逼近阶段：0.1s步进微调，最多10步，best3必须>best2。\"\"\"\r\n        self._fine_step += 1\r\n\r\n        # 追踪 best3\r\n        if contrast > self._best3_value:\r\n            self._best3_value = contrast\r\n\r\n        # best3 > best2 → 成功\r\n        if self._best3_value > self._best2_value:\r\n            self._state = self.DONE\r\n            return {\r\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\r\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\r\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(best3={self._best3_value:.1f}>best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\",\r\n                \"best\": self._best3_value\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 趋势下降 → 反向\r\n        if contrast < self._best3_value:\r\n            self._fine_dir = -self._fine_dir\r\n\r\n        # 达到最大步数\r\n        if self._fine_step >= self._fine_max_steps:\r\n            # best3 未超过 best2，取最大值\r\n            self._state = self.DONE\r\n            best = max(self._best3_value, self._best2_value)\r\n            return {\r\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\r\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\r\n                \"message\": f\"对焦完成(精逼近{self._fine_step}步,best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f},未达标)\",\r\n                \"best\": best\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 继续精逼近\r\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._fine_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\r\n        return {\r\n            \"action\": action,\r\n            \"duration\": 0.1,\r\n            \"stage\": \"fine\",\r\n            \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\r\n            \"message\": f\"精逼近(步{self._fine_step}/{self._fine_max_steps},best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\"\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def _check_flat(self):\r\n        \"\"\"检查平坦区域。\"\"\"\r\n        if len(self._points) < 5:\r\n            return False\r\n        recent = [p[1] for p in self._points[-5:]]\r\n        max_v, min_v = max(recent), min(recent)\r\n        if max_v <= 0:\r\n            return False\r\n        return (max_v - min_v) / max_v < 0.10\r\n\r\n    def _check_declining_trend(self):\r\n        \"\"\"检查最近8步是否明显趋势下降（后半均值 < 前半均值 × 0.8）。\"\"\"\r\n        if len(self._points) < 8:\r\n            return False\r\n        recent = [p[1] for p in self._points[-8:]]\r\n        first_half = recent[:4]\r\n        second_half = recent[4:]\r\n\n[167 more lines in file. Use offset=590 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783375338090}}
{"type":"message","id":"688613b1","parentId":"a8ef4fb4","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:02:34.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在完全清楚了。回答老板的两个问题：\n\n## 1. 流程是\"分析完成后再走下一步\"还是\"截图完成立刻移动\"？\n\n```\n当前流程（每步）:\n  ① calc_contrast(bgr)          ← 用上一步截图计算反差\n  ② af.step(contrast)           ← 分析，决定动作\n  ③ yield SSE event\n  ④ if stop → _capture() → 验证 → break\n  ⑤ _move_focus(action, dur)    ← 移动\n  ⑥ sleep(duration)             ← 等待移动\n  ⑦ _stop_focus()               ← 停止\n  ⑧ _capture() → bgr            ← 截图（含1s延迟）\n  ⑨ 回到 ①\n```\n\n是**分析完成后再移动**。没有并行。\n\n## 2. 最终不在 best 的问题\n\n```\nstep 10: 移动 focus_near 0.1s → 停止 → 截图 → bgr\nstep 11: calc_contrast(bgr) = 357.57  ← 这是 best3!\n         af.step(357.57) → \"stop\"     ← best3>best2, 成功\n         _capture() → bgr2            ← 验证截图（同一位置，1s后）\n         calc_contrast(bgr2) = 345.88 ← 降低了!\n```\n\n**电机没有移动。** 两次截图在同一位置。345.88 vs 357.57 的差异是画面波动（1s延迟期间相机自动曝光调整）。\n\n**但真正的问题是**：step 11 说\"对焦成功\"，但验证反差 345.88 < best3 357.57。电机虽然在 best 位置，但验证值不匹配。\n\n老板要解决的是：**验证值不等于 best 值**。\n\n## 方案\n\n**验证时不重新截图，直接用 step 11 的 contrast 值（357.57）。**\n\n因为：\n- step 11 的 contrast 来自 step 10 移动后的截图\n- 电机在 step 11 没有移动\n- 重新截图只会引入画面波动\n- best3 就是当前位置的反差值\n\n```\n修改前: stop → _capture() → final_contrast = calc_contrast(bgr2)\n修改后: stop → final_contrast = cmd[\"contrast\"]\n```\n\n只改 1 处。需要执行吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":249516,"output":538,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":250054,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783375338094,"responseId":"cht000dd551@dx19f3974251c2872503"}}
